com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmubi-streaming-rights-south-african-artist-william-kentridge-series-self-portrait-as-a-coffee-pot-1235944425%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmubi-streaming-rights-south-african-artist-william-kentridge-series-self-portrait-as-a-coffee-pot-1235944425%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmubi-streaming-rights-south-african-artist-william-kentridge-series-self-portrait-as-a-coffee-pot-1235944425%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sikkim%20Party%20Got%20Bonds%20Worth%20Rs%2050%20Lakh%20From%20Gujarat-Based%20Pharma%20Company%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2FSikkim-legislative-assembly-Photo-Government-of-Sikkim.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front%20(SDF)%2C%20when%20in%20power%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20state%20in%202018%2C%20received%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20from%20the%20Gujarat-based%20pharma%20company%20Alembic%20Pharmaceuticals%20Ltd%2C%20data%20uploaded%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%20has%20shown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20SDF%20furnished%20these%20details%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20to%20the%20ECI%20in%20May%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlembic%20Pharmaceuticals%20is%20based%20in%20Vadodara%20and%20deals%20with%20manufacturing%20generic%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20first%20featured%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitical-donations-2017-18-bjp-highest-congress%5C%22%3Ereport%20in%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%20compiled%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20based%20on%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20data%20on%20all%20donations%20above%20Rs%2020%2C000%20paid%20to%20the%20national%20parties%20during%20the%20FY%202017-2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20by%20the%20electoral%20reforms%20watchdog%20NGO%2C%20which%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20petitioners%20of%20the%20ongoing%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20had%20revealed%20that%20Alembic%20Pharmaceuticals%20had%20paid%20Rs%206%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20BJP%2C%20even%20while%20being%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20had%20not%20disclosed%20the%20names%20of%20its%20electoral%20bond%20funders%20to%20the%20ECI%20in%202023%2C%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20if%20Alembic%20funded%20the%20ruling%20party%20via%20bonds%20even%20after%20FY%202017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThough%20Alembic%20features%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20disclosures%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20established%20which%20party%20or%20parties%20ultimately%20received%20the%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20all%2C%20Alembic%20acquired%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%201.20%20crore%20between%20November%204%2C%202022%20and%20July%205%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202018%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20came%20up%20with%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20the%20ruling%20SDF%20in%20Sikkim%20received%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20from%20Alembic%20on%20October%2012.%20The%20party%20encashed%20five%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20each%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20a%20Court-Monitored%20Probe%20on%20Quid%20Pro%20Quo%20Involving%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Is%20Needed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-a-court-monitored-probe-on-quid-pro-quo-involving-electoral-bonds-is-needed%5C%22%3EWhy%20a%20Court-Monitored%20Probe%20on%20Quid%20Pro%20Quo%20Involving%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Is%20Needed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Alembic%2C%20exactly%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlembic%20runs%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20generic%20medicine%20production%20units%20for%20the%20domestic%20market%20in%20Sikkim%E2%80%99s%20Rangpo%20area.%20According%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjP4KCK0_2EAxUy4TgGHZ9cArYQFnoECA8QAw%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.business-standard.com%252Farticle%252Fcompanies%252Falembic-to-commission-sikkim-plant-this-fiscal-114110200689_1.html%2523%253A~%253Atext%253DVadodara%25252Dbased%252520pharma%252520company%252520Alembic%252Cyears%252520of%252520commissioning%252520the%252520facility.%26usg%3DAOvVaw1N2KTEHh-lWN4clQy-aa2y%26opi%3D89978449%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Furl%3Fsa%253Dt%2526rct%253Dj%2526q%253D%2526esrc%253Ds%2526source%253Dweb%2526cd%253D%2526cad%253Drja%2526uact%253D8%2526ved%253D2ahUKEwjP4KCK0_2EAxUy4TgGHZ9cArYQFnoECA8QAw%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.business-standard.com%25252Farticle%25252Fcompanies%25252Falembic-to-commission-sikkim-plant-this-fiscal-114110200689_1.html%252523%25253A~%25253Atext%25253DVadodara%2525252Dbased%25252520pharma%25252520company%25252520Alembic%25252Cyears%25252520of%25252520commissioning%25252520the%25252520facility.%2526usg%253DAOvVaw1N2KTEHh-lWN4clQy-aa2y%2526opi%253D89978449%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710848266859000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw16h3aFn4CJ7NB-i_ca60Y6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%202%2C%202014%2C%20Alembic%20was%20%E2%80%9Cset%20to%20commission%20its%20formula