ts%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fkya-baat-hai-yaar-virat-kohli-happy-to-be-back-at-rcb-den-ahead-of-ipl-2024%2Farticleshow%2F108592997.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice's%20%26quot%3BBroad%20Shoulders%26quot%3B%20Reply%20As%20Centre%20Flags%20Poll%20Bonds%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Centre%20and%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20flagged%20the%20social%20media%20fallout%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20landmark%20verdict%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20court's%20%26quot%3Bshoulders%20are%20broad%20enough%26quot%3B%20to%20tackle%20such%20commentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20CJI%20today%20asked%20SBI%20to%20disclose%20all%20details%20related%20to%20electoral%20bonds.%20It%20was%20hearing%20petitions%20that%20said%20the%20state-run%20bank%20had%20released%20%26quot%3Bincomplete%20data%26quot%3B%20on%20political%20funding%20through%20the%20now-scrapped%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20said%20the%20court%20must%20be%20informed%20about%20how%20its%20judgment%20is%20playing%20out.%20%26quot%3BThe%20witch-hunting%20has%20started%20on%20another%20level%20and%20not%20at%20the%20government%20level.%20Those%20before%20the%20court%20started%20giving%20press%20interviews%2C%20deliberately%20embarrassing%20the%20court.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%20There%20is%20a%20barrage%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20intended%20to%20cause%20embarrassment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistics%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bcan%20be%20twisted%20as%20people%20want%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBased%20upon%20twisted%20statistics%2C%20any%20kind%20of%20posts%20are%20made.%20Would%20your%20lordships%20consider%20issuing%20a%20direction%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20judges%2C%20we%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20and%20we%20work%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution.%20As%20judges%2C%20we%20are%20also%20discussed%20in%20social%20media%2C%20but%20as%20an%20institution%2C%20our%20shoulders%20are%20broad%20enough%20to%20deal%20with%20social%20media%20commentary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20cited%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20campaign%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20issue%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20doubled%20down%2C%20%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20I%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20criticism%20of%20a%20judgment.%20I%20said%20that%20as%20a%20judge%2C%20we%20cannot%20defend%20our%20judgments%2C%20once%20we%20deliver%20a%20judgment%2C%20it%20becomes%20public%20property.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20appearing%20for%20SBI%2C%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20is%20always%20behind%20us%2C%20with%20the%20petitioners%20saying%20they%20will%20take%20the%20SBI%20to%20task%2C%20haul%20them%20up%20in%20contempt%26quot%3B.%20Stressing%20that%20the%20bank%20is%20not%20holding%20back%20any%20information%2C%20Mr%20Salve%20flagged%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20series%20of%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL).%20%26quot%3BVoter%20knowing%20is%20one%20thing.%20But%20if%20there%20are%20PILs%20saying%20investigate%20this%20and%20that%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20is%20the%20intent%20of%20this%20court's%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Salve%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Bjudgments%20given%20for%20high%20Constitutional%20principles%20are%20used%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20what%20they%20are%20delivered%20for%2C%20unfortunately%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20was%20in%20for%20some%20tough%20talk%20today%2C%20when%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSBI's%20attitude%20seems%20to%20be%20'you%20tell%20us%20what%20to%20disclose%2C%20we%20will%20disclose'.%20That%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20fair.%20When%20we%20say%20'all%20details'%2C%20it%20includes%20all%20conceivable%20data.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20eventually%20asked%20the%20bank%20to%20disclose%20all%20details%2C%20including%20the%20alphanumeric%20number%20and%20serial%20number%2C%20if%20any%2C%20of%20the%20bonds%20redeemed.%20It%20also%20asked%20the%20SBI%20chairman%20to%20submit%20an%20affidavit%2C%20stating%20that%20no%20info%20has%20been%20withheld.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20was%20asked%20to%20upload%20the%20data%20received%20from%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710769500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjlc3in08_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_18_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-supreme-court-chief-justices-broad-shoulders-reply-as-centre-flags-poll-bonds-debate-5261177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Centre%20and%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20flagged%20the%20social%20media%20fallout%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20court's%20%26quot%3Bshoulders%20are%20broad%20enough%26quot%3B%20to%20tackle%20such%20commentary%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-supreme-court-chief-justices-broad-shoulders-reply-as-centre-flags-poll-bonds-debate-5261177%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-supreme-court-chief-justices-broad-shoulders-reply-as-centre-flags-poll-bonds-debate-5261177%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-supreme-court-chief-justices-b