ils%20throughout%20the%20day.%20For%20end-of-day%20full%20load%20-A%20dishwasher%20is%20used%20which%20is%20more%20water%20efficient%20than%20manual%20washing.%20Approx%20saving%3A360%20ltr%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20thread.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20waste%20water%20from%20RO%20is%20being%20collected%20in%20a%20container%20and%20this%20water%20is%20used%20for%20mopping%20and%20garden%20use.%20Approx%20saving%3A%2030%20lts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOthers%3A%20washing%20machine%20used%20once%20full%20load%20is%20achieved.%20Car%20wash%20has%20been%20stopped-%20every%20day%20dusting%20and%20alternate%20day%20wet%20cloth%20cleaning-%20the%20car%20still%20sparkles!%20Single%20push%20flush%20use%20Asked%20plumber%20to%20audit%20any%20pipe%20leakages.%20Approx%20saving%3A%2030%20lts%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmall%20initiatives%20help%20save%20600%20ltrs%20per%20day%20in%20our%20household%20of%204.%20Plus%20there%20is%20ZERO%20impact%20on%20our%20lifestyle.%20Small%20savings%20add%20up%20to%20big%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESmall%20steps%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWater%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Water%3C%2Fa%3E%20conservation%20at%20home.%20Though%20we%20have%20been%20extremely%20prudent%20with%20water%20usage%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20there%20is%20always%20scope%20for%20improvement.%20Sharing%20our%20household%20experience%F0%9F%91%87%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20Divya%20Sharma%20(%40divya_sharmaMD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdivya_sharmaMD%2Fstatus%2F1769303273402782160%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20post%20collected%20over