n%20front%20of%20their%20house%2C%20a%20public%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fcouple-thrashed-for-parking-car-near-neighbours-house-in-bengaluru-5262984%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fcouple-thrashed-for-parking-car-near-neighbours-house-in-bengaluru-5262984%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fcouple-thrashed-for-parking-car-near-neighbours-house-in-bengaluru-5262984%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Nadeem's%20Struggle%20To%20Buy%20New%20Javelin%2C%20Neeraj%20Says%20%26quot%3BHard%20To%20Believe%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Chopra%20and%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20are%20two%20of%20the%20brightest%20javelin%20throwers%20to%20have%20emerged%20from%20Asia%20in%20recent%20time.%20In%20competitions%2C%20the%20duo%20has%20been%20known%20to%20push%20each%20other%20for%20more%20success.%20Off%20the%20pitch%2C%20they%20have%20been%20known%20for%20their%20bonhomie%20and%20camaraderie.%20They%20may%20be%20fierce%20competitors%20but%20have%20a%20healthy%20respect%20for%20each%20other.%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20and%20India's%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20are%20javelin%20superstars%20in%20their%20own%20right%20and%20a%20symbol%20of%20perfect%20friendship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20and%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20are%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20upcoming%20outdoor%20season.%20While%20Chopra%20is%20currently%20training%20in%20Turkey%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20Nadeem's%20preparations%20have%20hit%20a%20'snag'.%20The%20Pakistani%20recently%20said%20he%20is%20struggling%20to%20acquire%20an%20international%20standard%20javelin%20for%20many%20years%20and%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Busing%20one%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20to%20eight%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%2C%20the%20world%20and%20defending%20Olympic%20champion%2C%20is%20rather%20surprised%20to%20hear%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20chat%20with%20SAI%20Media%20recently%2C%20Chopra%2C%20who%20competed%20with%20Nadeem%20in%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Championships%20in%20Budapest%20last%20year%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20he%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20get%20a%20new%20javelin.%20Given%20his%20credentials%2C%20this%20should%20not%20be%20a%20big%20issue%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20Nadeem%2C%20who%20finished%20second%20behind%20Chopra%20in%20Budapest%2C%20was%20recently%20quoted%20in%20the%20media%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20now%20got%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20the%20javelin%20is%20damaged%20and%20I%20have%20asked%20the%20national%20federation%20and%20my%20coach%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%20before%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20started%20off%20in%202015%2C%20competing%20in%20international%20events%20I%20got%20this%20javelin%20%E2%80%A6%20for%20an%20international%20athlete%20aiming%20to%20win%20a%20medal%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20you%20need%20proper%20equipment%20and%20training%20facilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%2C%20whose%20entire%20training%20and%20international%20tours%20are%20funded%20by%20the%20Indian%20sports%20ministry's%20Target%20Olympic%20Podium%20Scheme%2C%20feels%20that%20Nadeem%20is%20the%20pride%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20must%20be%20supported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%2090.18m%20throw%2C%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20had%20created%20a%20new%20javelin%20throw%20record%20at%20the%202022%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20Birmingham%20to%20finish%20on%20top%20of%20the%20podium.%20It%20ended%20Pakistan's%2060-year%20wait%20for%20a%20CWG%20gold%20medal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20be%20that%20he%20(Arshad)%20doesn't%20have%20the%20means%20to%20buy%20a%20javelin.%20He%20is%20a%20champion%20and%20must%20be%20doing%20some%20brand%20endorsements.%20I%20reckon%20he%20has%20earned%20a%20bit%20of%20money%20too.%20But%20having%20said%20that%2C%20his%20government%20can%20look%20at%20Arshad's%20need%20and%20support%20him%20just%20like%20how%20my%20government%20is%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20Arshad%20is%20top%20javelin%20thrower%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20the%20javelin%20makers%20will%20be%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20sponsor%20him%20and%20provide%20what%20he%20wants.%20This%20is%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20from%20my%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20the%20javelin%20competition%20at%20the%20upcoming%20Paris%20Olympics%20could%20see%20a%20strong%20Asian%20field.%20Chopra%20and%20Kishore%20Jena%20will%20spearhead%20India%20while%20Nadeem%2C%20who%20finished%20fifth%20in%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20will%20hope%20to%20replicate%20another%2090%20metre-plus%20throw%20in%20Paris%20and%20pose%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20a%20sport%20usually%20dominated%20by%20Europeans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20had%20a%20serious%20elbow%20operation%20in%20UK.%20Last%20year%2C%20Nadeem%20had%20a%20niggling%20knee%20operation%20done%20and%20skipped%20the%20Hangzhou%20Asian%20Games%20where%20Chopra%20won%20the%20gold.%20The%20outdoor%20javelin%20season%20starts%20with%20the%20Doha%20leg%20of%20the%20Diamond%20League%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710768120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fj0gp3j6o_neeraj-chopra-arshad-nadeem-afp_625x300_28_August_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fon-pakistans-arshad-nadeems-struggle-to-buy-new-javelin-neeraj-chopra-says-hard-to-believe-gives-advice-5262967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Off%20the%20pitch%2C%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20and%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20have%20been%20known%20for%20their%20bonhomie%20and%20camaraderie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%2