%2C%20the%20top%20cop%20of%20a%20state%20that%20has%20seen%20several%20instances%20of%20poll-related%20violence%20in%20recent%20years.%20Vivek%20Sahay%2C%20who%20was%20Director-General%20and%20Commandant%20of%20the%20Home%20Guards%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20new%20Bengal%20DGP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20re-shuffle%2C%20not%20an%20uncommon%20move%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20before%20major%20polls%2C%20also%20included%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Uttarakhand%20Home%20Secretaries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20senior%20officials%20attached%20to%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Mizoram%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Iqbal%20Singh%20Chahal%2C%20who%20is%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%2C%20and%20other%20officials%20in%20municipalities%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20was%20removed%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%3B%20the%20ECI%20on%20Saturday%20said%20voting%20will%20begin%20on%20April%2019%20and%20run%20over%20seven%20phases%20till%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20first%20re-jig%20by%20the%20ECI%20since%20it%20announced%20polling%20dates%2C%20and%20it%C2%A0came%20after%20a%20meeting%20of%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20and%20his%20two%20associates%2C%20the%20newly-appointed%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%20and%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu.%20The%20poll%20panel%20has%20underlined%20its%20commitment%20to%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20all%20parties%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20as%20well%20as%20state%20by-polls%20over%20the%20next%20100%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20personnel%20removed%20were%20found%20to%20be%20holding%20dual%20charge%20in%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20respective%20chief%20ministers%20of%20each%20state%2C%20and%20this%20could%20compromise%2C%20or%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20compromising%2C%20required%20neutrality%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20law-and-order%20before%2C%20during%20and%20after%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Sanjay%20Prasad%20-%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20-%20had%20been%20given%20additional%20charge%20of%20the%20Home%20Department%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20removal%20of%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20by%20the%20opposition%20as%20be%20close%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20party.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20also%20questioned%20the%20last-minute%20re-shuffle%20of%20senior%20officials%20so%20close%20to%20an%20election%2C%20arguing%20it%20hampers%20prep%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20leader%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20accused%20the%20saffron%20party%20of%20%26quot%3Btrying%20their%20best%20to%20grab%20organisations%20like%20the%20ECI...%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20its%20success%20when%20the%20state%20votes%20across%20five%20phases%20beginning%20April%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20help%20their%20state%20unit%20because%20they%20know%2C%20in%20the%20election%2C%20BJP%20will%20be%20defeated%20in%20most%20of%20Bengal's%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20may%20transfer%20a%20few%20officers%20but%20the%20public%20is%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20%3Cem%3Edidi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(as%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20referred%20to)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20has%20frequently%20witnessed%20violence%20during%20polling%20season%3B%20in%20June%20last%20year%20over%20a%20dozen%20people%20were%20killed%20across%20the%20state%20as%20voting%20for%20a%20panchayat%20election%20was%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparties-condemn-violence-in-bengal-panchayat-poll-violence-bjp-seeks-