%20excellence%2C%20into%20a%20lackey%2C%20denying%20it%20any%20kind%20of%20autonomy.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20details%20available%20so%20far%20from%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20can%20be%20discerned%20that%20the%20present%20dispensation%20has%20done%20more%20harm%20to%20the%20Indian%20banking%20system%20than%20any%20of%20their%20predecessors!%20SBI%20has%20now%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20sidekick%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20has%20tried%20to%20force%20it%20to%20the%20ledger%20era%2C%20by%20arm-twisting%20it%20to%20delay%20publishing%20details%20regarding%20the%20purchase%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20destruction%20of%20our%20institutions%20has%20been%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20see.%20Deeply%20troubling%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20the%20immunity%20the%20government%20now%20enjoys.%20What%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20are%20statements%20by%20grandees%20of%20the%20establishment.%20The%20people%20in%20power%20are%20made%20to%20look%20beyond%20reproach.%20If%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20were%20alive%20today%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20found%20his%20way%20into%20our%20current%20discourse%20because%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20conventional%20notions%20of%20power%20or%20power%20politics.%20Evidently%2C%20very%20few%20entities%20want%20to%20call%20out%20the%20government%20for%20having%20put%20in%20place%20a%20scheme%20called%20electoral%20bonds%20that%20was%2C%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20designed%20to%20enable%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20with%20its%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20system%20that%20has%20a%20corrosive%20effect%20on%20democracy%20because%20big%20corporations%20are%20allowed%20to%20not%20only%20flourish%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20cannibalising%20competition%20within%20the%20industry%20but%20also%20prompt%20the%20government%20to%20tweak%20policies%20in%20their%20favour.%20The%20apex%20court%20in%20the%20country%20had%20ruled%20against%20it%2C%20but%20the%20argument%20being%20zealously%20handed%20out%20to%20whitewash%20the%20government%20by%20projecting%20a%20corny%20argument%20is%20the%20following%3A%20politicians%20and%20businesses%20have%20always%20had%20thick%20ties.%20At%20no%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20free%20India%20have%20we%20seen%20such%20misgivings%20about%20reporting%20any%20such%20collusion%20or%20sweeping%20them%20under%20the%20carpet.%20We%20must%20be%20more%20cautious%20as%20crony%20capitalism%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20stunt%20not%20only%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%20but%20also%20to%20slow%20down%20its%20growth%2C%20notwithstanding%20tall%20claims%20of%20achieving%20economic%20superpower%20status%20and%20lofty%20goals%20of%20a%20five-trillion-dollar%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvoters-must-not-remain-in-the-dark-about-buyers-of-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-4000-crore%5C%22%3EVoters%20Must%20Not%20Remain%20in%20the%20Dark%20About%20Buyers%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Worth%20Rs%204%2C000%20Crore%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20most%20important%20facets%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20could%20be%20summarised%20as%20follows%3A%20a%20witch-hunt%20by%20central%20agencies%2C%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%2C%20or%2C%20if%20not%2C%20subsequent%20rewards%20by%20the%20beneficiary.%20There%20are%2043%20companies%20which%20indulged%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20within%20a%20few%20months%20of%20their%20incorporation.%20Shell%20companies%20galore%2C%20existing%20solely%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20bonds.%2019%20companies%2C%20which%20were%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2F18-of-19-firms-marked-high-risk-by-finance-ministry-that-bought-electoral-bonds-went-off-future-list%5C%22%3Ehigh%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20potential%20money%20laundering%20by%20the%20finance%20ministry%2C%20collectively%20contributed%20a%20whopping%20Rs%202%2C717%20crore.%20Curiously%2C%2018%20of%20them%20were%20later%20exonerated%20and%20got%20out%20of%20the%20said%20high%20risk%20bracket.%20In%20any%20other%20democracy%2C%20if%20such%20blatant%20transgressions%20had%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20concerned%20agencies%20would%20have%20already%20stepped%20in%20on%20the%20bond%20trail%20to%20unearth%20the%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20rightly%20feared%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20could%20have%20changed%20hands%20before%20reaching%20the%20actual%20beneficiary.%20There%20is%20no%20guarantee%20that%20foreign%20companies%20didn%E2%80%99t%20meddle%20with%20these%20instruments%20having%20far%20reaching%20consequences%20for%20our%20democracy.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20abrogation%20of%20ceiling%20of%207.5%25%20of%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20average%20net%20profits%20of%20a%20company%20for%20political%20donations%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20insulate%20bonds%20from%20the%20provision%20of%20preventing%20foreign%20companies%20from%20political%20donations%20as%20per%20the%20FCRA%20have%20devastating%20ramifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20brazen%20acts%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20unchallenged.%20Even%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20biggest%20capitalist%20society%20in%20the%20world%2C%20political%20funding%20is%20far%20more%20transparent%20than%20it%20is%20in%20India%2C%20where%20the%20government%20knows%20who%20gives%20them%20money%20and%20who%20gives%20their%20political%20opponents%20the%20money%2C%20and%20where%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20is%20found%20to%20unleash%20central%20agencies%20in%20a%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20all%20norms.%20These%20central%20agencies%20are%20put%20to%20good%20use%20by%20the%20ruling%20government%20with%20impunity%20in%20extracting%20consent%20from%20not%20only%20rivals%20but%20also%20corporations.%20It%20was%20independent%20media%20groups%20that%20brought%20to%20centre%20stage%20huge%20purchases%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20by%20a%20large%20number%20of%20companies%20that%20were%20raided%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials.%20Governmental%20behaviour%20amounts%20to%20the%20economic%20espionage%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties.%20We%20cannot%20afford%20to%20assume%20that%20democracy%20is%20a%20winner-takes-all%20affair.%20Democracy%20is%20not%20an%20ancient%20Colosseum%20where%20gladiators%20spar%20to%20win%20and%20stay%20alive.%20It%20is%20much%20more%20sophisticated%20and%20nuanced%20than%20that.%20The%20opposition%20enjoys%20tremendous%20rights%2C%20and%20those%20are%20all%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Left%20parties%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20voice%20against%20such%20avaricious%20tendencies%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%20The%20Left%20is%20often%20the%20first%20to%20make%20the%20right%20noises%20against%20crony%20capitalism%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20file%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme.%20In%20line%20with%20its%20progressive%20politics%2C%20it%20had%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20opposing%20tooth%20and%20nail%20various%20moves%20by%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20including%20its%20moves%20to%20castrate%20the%20SBI.%20Some%20people%20are%20busy%20hanging%20a%20bad%20name%20on%20Communist%20parties%20and%20calling%20them%20anti-nationals.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20not%20forget%20that%20while%20other%20leaders%20of%20the%20national%20movement%20vacillated%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20was%20a%20Communist%20who%20coined%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%9CPoorna%20Swaraj%E2%80%9D%20in%201921.%20The%20undivided%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20was%20the%20only%20entity%20that%20backed%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Royal%20Naval%20Uprising%20of%201946%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20made%20the%20British%20deeply%20insecure%20about%20continuing%20to%20rule%20India%20with%20disloyal%20armed%20forces.%20The%20Left%20continues%20to%20live%20up%20to%20those%20ideals%20although%20we%20are%20short%20in%20numbers%20