ong%20central%20leader%20and%20no%20clear%20leadership%20hierarchy%20or%20party%20structure.%20One%20consequence%20is%20that%20nobody%20is%20able%20to%20say%20which%20leader(s)%20took%20the%20decision%20to%20go%20with%20the%20SIC.%20This%2C%20when%20at%20least%20two%20top%20lawyer-leaders%20confirm%20Imran%20Khan%20had%20decided%20in%20favour%20of%20Majlis%20Wahdat-e-Muslimeen%20or%20the%20Maulana%20Sheerani-led%20JUI-S.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20physical%20isolation%20is%20in%20place%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time%2C%20similar%20problems%20may%20crop%20up%20in%20decision-making%20and%20will%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20party%20and%20its%20well-being.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20a%20larger-than-life%20leader%20for%20his%20party%2C%20but%20is%20it%20prudent%20that%20there%20is%20no%20clear%20second%20in%20command%20or%20even%20a%20%E2%80%98committee%20of%20elders%E2%80%99%20to%20hold%20the%20fort%20in%20his%20absence%3F%20Apart%20from%20high%20court%20debacles%2C%20there%20are%20also%20murmurings%20of%20discontent%20over%20KP%20cabinet%20positions%20and%20the%20party%20nominations%20for%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ground%20reality%20facing%20PML-N%20leader%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20may%20be%20differently%20constructed%2C%20but%20in%20effect%20he%20has%20also%20been%20blocked%20from%20taking%20key%20decisions%2C%20even%20when%20his%20party%20is%20a%20major%20coalition%20partner%20in%20government.%20Anyone%20who%20knows%20how%20things%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20PML-N%20till%20now%20need%20look%20no%20further%20than%20the%20federal%20cabinet%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreed%20that%20he%20may%20have%20been%20given%20the%20consolation%20prize%20of%20having%20his%20daughter%20placed%20at%20the%20helm%20in%20Punjab%3B%20however%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20slots%20in%20Islamabad%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1820748%5C%22%3Ehasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20the%20man%20on%20whom%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20has%20not%20been%20willing%20to%20compromise%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENawaz%20Sharif%20has%20complete%20and%20unflinching%20faith%20in%20the%20financial%20nous%20and%20expertise%20of%20Ishaq%20Dar%2C%20as%20was%20evident%20during%20his%20own%20tenure%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20when%20Dar%20served%20as%20the%20finance%20minister%2C%20and%20also%20under%20the%2016-month%20PDM%20coalition%2C%20when%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20insisted%20on%20the%20sacking%20of%20Miftah%20Ismail%20and%20replacing%20him%20with%20Dar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20returned%20expecting%20to%20be%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20four-time%20prime%20minister%20and%20shape%20the%20future%20according%20to%20his%20worldview%20and%20vision.%20Now%2C%20he%20has%20to%20live%20with%20seeing%20his%20first%20choice%20as%20finance%20minister%20having%20been%20shunted%20to%20the%20Foreign%20Office.%20And%20this%20amidst%20the%20worst%20economic%20crisis%20the%20country%20has%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20veteran%20politician%20and%20successful%20businessman%2C%20Sharif%20knows%20well%20how%20his%20influence%20in%20decision-making%20will%20ebb%20dramatically%20when%20his%20own%20man%20isn%E2%80%99t%20in%20control%20of%20the%20purse%20strings.%20He%20scuppered%20Miftah%E2%80%99s%20Ismail%E2%80%99s%20planned%20structural%20reform%20because%20he%20said%20it%20inflicted%20too%20much%20pain%20on%20the%20poor%20Pakistani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%E2%80%99ll%20witness%20that%20pain%20being%20forced%20on%20the%20people%20again%20and%20be%20no%20more%20than%20a%20silent%20bystander.%20Despite%20their%20dilemmas%20rooted%20in%20the%20same%20source%2C%20will%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20ever%20see%20eye%20to%20eye%20on%20the%20need%20for%20a%20genuine%20democratic%20transition%20in%20the%20country%20or%20will%20they%20keep%20playing%20for%20tiny%20gains%20and%20no%20more%3F%20This%2