0blueberry%2C%20and%20cranberry%20imports%20into%20India%20skyrocketed%20to%20870%20tonnes%20in%202022%20%E2%80%93%20indicating%20a%20surge%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indexbox.io%2Fsearch%2Fprice-for-raspberry-blackberry-blueberry-and-cranberry-india%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202022%252C%2520raspberry%252C%2520blackberry%252C%2C616%2525%2520against%2520the%2520previous%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E148%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Highbush%20Blueberry%20Council%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fdemand-for-us-blueberry-rising-in-india%2Farticle34852525.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSHBC%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20imports%20of%20blueberries%20in%20fresh%20and%20dried%20forms%20grew%20from%20almost%20zero%20in%202009%20to%201%2C900%20tonnes%20in%202020%2C%20making%20India%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20top%20importers%20of%20blueberries.%20This%20trade%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20rate%20of%20around%2030%20percent%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20numbers%20are%20rising%20annually%2C%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Keya%20Salot%20has%20stepped%20up%20to%20bring%20these%20numbers%20down%20to%20some%20extent.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202021-22%2C%20India%20was%20importing%20%242.2%20billion%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313743%2Fchethan-shetty-quit-corporate-job-to-become-farmer-in-bellare-mangaluru-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20vegetables.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20really%20a%20good%20number.%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20the%20sector%20to%20cultivate%20these%20exotic%20varieties%20locally.%20By%20doing%20this%2C%20it%20would%20also%20make%20them%20affordable%20for%20consumers%20beyond%20metros%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20these%20exotic%20berries.%20Today%2C%20she%20has%20scaled%20up%20the%20production%20on%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20estimates%20a%20production%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blueberries%20and%20raspberries%20are%20cultivated%20largely%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-4-1710700215-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345042%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBlueberries%20and%20raspberries%20are%20cultivated%20largely%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20innovative%20methods%20that%20helped%20her%20cultivate%20berries%20in%20the%20harsh%20weather%20conditions%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuit%20law%20to%20become%20a%20farmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Keya%20was%20a%20lawyer%20by%20profession.%20After%20pursuing%20law%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Government%20Law%20College%2C%20she%20continued%20her%20practice%20with%20law%20firms%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20until%20she%20understood%20her%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20pursuing%20law%20was%20always%20to%20later%20focus%20on%20entrepreneurship.%20But%20before%20that%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20good%20access%20to%20the%20legal%20framework%20to%20build%20a%20successful%20business.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20an%20impactful%20sector%20to%20create%20a%20very%20purpose-driven%20entrepreneurship%20programme%20which%20would%20not%20only%20benefit%20me%20personally%20but%20would%20also%20benefit%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2032-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20she%20took%20a%20break%20from%20work%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritties%20of%20farming%20as%20she%20did%20not%20have%20any%20agricultural%20background.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20Keya%20started%20growing%20about%2030%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20in%20a%20vertical%20set-up%20made%20on%20the%20terrace.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20supplying%20them%20to%20restaurants%2C%20and%20within%20six%20months%2C%20she%20on-boarded%2050%20clients.%20This%20boosted%20her%20confidence%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20establish%20retail%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20this%20transition%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20on%20the%20kinds%20of%20crops%20grown%20in%20other%20countries%20that%20had%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20traction%20in%20agriculture.%20Compared%20to%20countries%20in%20South%20and%20Central%20America%2C%20India%20has%20not%20graduated%20beyond%20growing%20major%20basic%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20and%20wheat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20exotic%20berries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-1-1-1710699243-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345039%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20Keya%20set%20up%20Farm2Fam%20to%20cultivate%20exotic%20berries.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20despite%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20population%20being%20dependent%20on%20agriculture%2C%20we%20are%20not%20able%20to%20produce%20high-value%20crops.%20We%20needed%20to%20choose%20crops%20that%20will%20get%20a%20slightly%20longer%20cycle%20but%20will%20give%20definitive%20returns%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20research%2C%20Keya%20zeroed%20down%20to%20cultivating%20the%20crop%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F34505%2Fraspberry-pi-kits-for-school-children-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan