68w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkeya-salot-2-1710699316-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345040%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKeya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20cultivate%20them%20in%20the%20tropical%20climate%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Keya%20opted%20for%20the%20tunnel%20method%20of%20cultivation%20that%20overcame%20the%20drawbacks%20of%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20required%20to%20protect%20crops%20like%20raspberries%20and%20blueberries%20from%20extreme%20temperatures.%20Currently%2C%20India%20only%20has%20poly%20houses%20as%20an%20infrastructure%20for%20protected%20cultivation%2C%20and%20in%20geographical%20climates%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20we%20need%20protection%20from%20harsh%20conditions%20rather%20than%20adding%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20developed%20our%20own%20low-cost%20tunnel%20structures%20for%20growing%20these%20berries%20where%20we%20can%20add%20or%20remove%20the%20plastic%20cover%20as%20per%20the%20weather%20requirements%20and%20maintain%20ideal%20temperature%20conditions%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20plants.%20With%20this%2C%20we%20can%20now%20provide%20a%20warmer%20climate%20during%20the%20winter%20nights%20and%20cooler%20conditions%20for%20growth%20during%20the%20summer%20days%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20protecting%20the%20crops%20from%20rain.%20This%20technique%20has%20its%20origin%20in%20the%20European%20countries%20where%20they%20use%20the%20structure%20to%20protect%20the%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeya%20installed%20low-cost%20tunnels%20in%20about%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20farm%20and%20is%20cultivating%20at%20least%20seven%20varieties%20of%20exotic%20berries.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22no