%20setting%20up%20the%20farm%20business%20in%20Talegaon%2C%20Pune%2C%20Keya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20access%20to%20land%20was%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20us%20as%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20convince%20a%20farmer%20to%20lease%20their%20land%20to%20a%20city%20dweller.%20As%20you%20do%20not%20have%20a%20base%20in%20a%20village%2C%20it%20invites%20a%20lot%20of%20aversion.%20But%20after%203%20to%204%20months%20of%20trying%20our%20hands%2C%20we%20got%20our%20first%20piece%20of%20land.%20It%20took%20some%20time%20to%20build%20trust%20among%20the%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20has%20expanded%20the%20production%20on%2020%20acres%20of%20land%20and%20expects%20a%20bountiful%20harvest%20of%20at%20least%20135%20tonnes%20of%20berries%20this%20season.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20she%20has%20collaborated%20with%20delivery%20partners%20like%20Swiggy%20and%20Zepto%2C%20and%20supermarkets%20like%20Star%20Bazaar%2C%20KisanKonnect%2C%20Reliance%20Retail%2C%20and%20Nature%E2%80%99s%20Basket%20to%20deliver%20the%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20transition%20from%20being%20a%20lawyer%20to%20an%20innovative%20farmer%2C%20Keya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20perception%20that%20agriculture%20is%20not%20a%20profitable%20business.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20our%20economy%20rests%20on%20it.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20people%20with%20exposure%20to%20change%20this%20perception%20rather%20than%20fear%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20if%20I%20had%20only%20practiced%20law%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20impact%20that%20I%20would%20have%20had%20would%20have%20been%20much%20smaller%20than%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20having%20today%20in%20terms%20of%20cultivating%20new%20kinds%20of%20crops%20by%20using%20innovative%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Keya%20Salot.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1