2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Media%20Summits%20Are%20Busy%20Massaging%20the%20Ego%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20That%20Too%20on%20Election%20Eve%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131044%2FGINxSf5WcAAw8wr.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EClose%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20one%20media%20%E2%80%98summit%E2%80%99%20that%20offered%20a%20platform%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20wax%20eloquent%20on%20his%20leadership%20a%20day%20after%20election%20dates%20were%20announced%2C%20yet%20another%20media%20event%20is%20being%20staged%20this%20week%20offering%20Modi%20primetime%20real%20estate%20for%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20such%20media%20events%20began%20in%20the%201990s%20it%20was%20the%20normal%20practice%20that%20apart%20from%20speakers%20from%20the%20government%20there%20would%20also%20be%20speakers%20from%20opposition%20political%20parties.%20Sometimes%20there%20would%20be%20a%20panel%20of%20speakers%20with%20both%20the%20political%20party%20in%20government%20and%20ones%20in%20opposition%20represented.%20That%20was%20the%20era%20in%20which%20a%20plural%20and%20liberal%20democracy%20was%20thriving.%20Today%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20place%20for%20such%20balance%20even%20in%20media%20hosted%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%202014%2C%20the%20general%20practice%20at%20all%20such%20events%20was%20to%20have%20at%20least%20one%20speaker%20from%20an%20opposition%20political%20party%20to%20balance%20the%20views%20of%20speakers%20from%20the%20government.%20During%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20decade%20in%20office%20the%20media%20favourite%20in%20the%200pposition%20who%20would%20be%20invited%20to%20speak%2C%20after%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20some%20of%20his%20senior%20ministers%20have%20spoken%2C%20would%20often%20be%20Arun%20Jaitley%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20It%20was%20considered%20the%20normal%20thing%20to%20do.%20Allow%20the%20opposition%20to%20have%20its%20say%2C%20once%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20has%20had%20its%20views%20put%20across.%20Alas%2C%20that%20no%20longer%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20media%20event%20the%20hosts%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20did%20invite%20speakers%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20including%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20and%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%2C%20even%20if%20the%20publishers%20were%20unapologetic%20about%20their%20support%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20ease%20with%20which%20they%20would%20rubbish%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20week%E2%80%99s%20event%2C%20hosted%20by%20%3Cem%3ECNN-News18%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20organisers%20have%20been%20even%20more%20blatant%20in%20their%20partisanship.%20All%20the%20politicians%20invited%20are%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20No%20one%20from%20any%20opposition%20party%20is%20listed%20as%20a%20speaker.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20News18%20format%20is%20now%20the%20norm%20for%20most%20such%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20among%20the%20public%20are%20aware%20of%20why%20media%20organisations%20host%20such%20events.%20I%20was%20made%20aware%20of%20this%20when%20I%20became%20an%20editor.%20From%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20media%20managements%20all%20such%20events%20are%20revenue%20raising%20opportunities.%20The%20money%20spent%20on%20hosting%20the%20event%20is%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20is%20raised%20from%20corporate%20sponsors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%20the%20hotel%20hosting%20the%20event%20is%20itself%20a%20sponsor%20so%20there%20is%20no%20money%20to%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20venue.%20Corporate%20sponsors%20are%20offered%20the%20privilege%20of%20their%20nominees%20being%20seated%20in%20the%20front%20and%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20main%20sponsor%2C%20an%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20the%20chief%20guest%20privately%20in%20an%20ante%20room%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20before%20or%20after%20the%20session.%20Corporate%20CEOs%20are%20unabashed%20in%20the%20demands%20they%20make%20in%20return%20for%20event%20sponsorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20such%20events%20help%20raise%20revenues%20through%20sponsorship%2C%20media%20organisations%20classify%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98profit%20centres%E2%80%99.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20took%20the%20lead%20in%20hosting%20such%20media%20events.%20Many%20others%20followed%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20types%20of%20such%20events%20hosted%20by%20media.%20First%2C%20the%20talk%20shops%20where%20speeches%20are%20made%20through%20the%20day%20and%20an%20opportunity%20for%20networking%20is%20offered%20over%20cocktails%20and%20dinner.%20Second%2C%20award%20events%20where%20media%20give%20out%20all%20manner%20of%20awards%2C%20often%20aimed%20at%20massaging%20the%20ego%20of%20the%20chosen%20political%2C%20bureaucratic%20and%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20of%20eminent%20persons%20is%20tasked%20to%20decide%20the%20awardees%2C%20but%20sometimes%20the%20host%20organisation%20indicates%20its%20preference%20to%20helpful%20juries.%20While%20some%20reputed%20media%20organisations%20ensure%20transparency%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20awardees%2C%20even%20they%20view%20the%20entire%20initiative%20as%20one%20that%20helps%20raise%20revenues%20and%20enhances%20brand%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20aware%20from%20personal%20knowledge%20that%20in%20some%20media%20organisations%20professional%20journalists%20keep%20their%20distance%20in%20raising%20sponsorship%20funds%20and%20leave%20this%20task%20to%20be%20performed%20by%20managers.%20There%20are%20others%20that%20actively%20seek%20journalists%E2%80%99%20help%20in%20this%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20business%20logic%20of%20media%20events%20and%20awards%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20we%20now%20have%20far%20too%20many%20of%20them%20and%20most%20events%20have%20become%20networking%20opportunities.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20devaluation%20of%20the%20awards%20presented%20given%20that%20the%20truly%20deserving%20are%20few%20and%20have%20already%20been%20awarded.%20But%20then%2C%20the%20revenues%20being%20raised%20are%20still%20not%20that%20small%20because%20every%20new%20generation%20of%20CEOs%2C%20%E2%80%98influencers%E2%80%99%2C%20social%20butterflies%20and%20celebrities%20want%20an%20opportunity%20to%20rub%20shoulders%2C%20or%20at%20least%20shake%20hands%2C%20or%20even%20do%20a%20Bharatiya%20%3Cem%3Enamaste%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20power%20elite%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20be%20photographed%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20media%20organisations%20have%20unabashedly%20declared%20themselves%20to%20be%20in%20the%20business%20of%20business%20and%20not%20in%20the%20business%20of%20news%20and%20analysis%2C%20even%20those%20that%20claim%20to%20promote%20%E2%80%98journalism%20of%20courage%E2%80%99%20have%20become%20platforms%20for%20the%20powerful%20to%20voice%20their%20opinions%20to%20select%20elite%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinisters%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%20have%20become%20so%20careful%20about%20where%20they%20speak%20and%20what%20they%20say%20that%20such%20media%20hosted%20interactions%20have%20become%20nothing%20more%20than%20opportunities%20for%20free%20and%20uninterrupted%20propaganda%20and%20publicity.%20Why%20pay%20for%20advertising%20when%20the%20news%20pages%20can%20do%20all%20the%20ego-massaging%20one%20seeks%20for%20free%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETailpiece%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20In%202007%2C%20when%20%3Cem%3ECNN-IBN%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eawarded%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20of%20the%20Year%20Award%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20attend%20the%20award%20event%20saying%20that%20a%20prime%20minister%20should%20not%20be%20grateful%20to%20any%20media%20organisation%20for%20such%20recognition.%20Rather%2C%20he%20said%20to%20me%2C%20if%20he%20is%20being%20recognised%20as%20such%20by%20the%20media%20then%20it%20must%20be%20because%20the%20media%20had%20a%20positive%20view%20of%20his%20leadership.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20told%20me%2C%20that%20I%20should%20be%20getting%20an%20award!%20So%2C%20on%20his%20instructions%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ECNN-IBN%3C%2Fem%3E%20awards%20function%20and%2C%20as%20his%20media%20advisor%2C%20thanked%20the%20jury%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESanjaya%20Baru%20is%20an%20economist%2C%20a%20former%20newspaper%20editor%2C%20a%20best-selling%20author%2C%20and%20former%20adviser%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710759602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131044%2FGINxSf5WcAAw8wr.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fahead-of-lok-sabha-polls-media-summits-are-busy-ego-massaging-prime-minister-modi-and-his-ministers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20this%20week's%20event%2C%20hosted%20by%20CNN-News18%2C%20all%20the%20politicians%20invited%20are%20from%20the%20BJP.%20No%20one%20from%20any%20opposition%20party%20is%20advertised%20as%20a%20speaker.%20Even%20those%20that%20claim%20to%20promote%20'journalism%20of%20courage'%20have%20become%20platforms%20for%20the%20powerful%20to%20voice%20their%20opinions%20to%20select%20elite%20audiences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fahead-of-lok-sabha-polls-media-summits-are-busy-ego-massaging-prime-minister-modi-and-his-ministers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Xi%20congratulates%20Putin%20on%20re-election%2C%20says%20ties%20will%20strengthen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710759550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-10858