Mr%20Nedumpara%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20said%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%20%26quot%3Bwas%20not%20a%20justiciable%20issue%20at%20all%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20policy%20matter%20and%20not%20for%20the%20courts%20to%20get%20into.%20That%20is%20why%20people%20feel%20this%20judgment%20was%20given%20behind%20their%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20spoke%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20kept%20asking%20him%20to%20pause%20and%20listen.%20Mr%20Nedumpara%2C%20however%2C%20went%20on%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20citizen%20of%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20firmly%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20second%2C%20don't%20shout%20at%20me.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20defensive%2C%20Mr%20Nedumpara%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20no%2C%20I%20am%20very%20soft.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20went%20on%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20Hyde%20Park%20corner%20meeting%2C%20you%20are%20in%20the%20court.%20You%20want%20to%20move%20an%20application%2C%20file%20an%20application.%20You%20have%20got%20my%20decision%20as%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20we%20are%20not%20hearing%20you.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20file%20an%20application%2C%20move%20it%20on%20the%20email.%20That's%20the%20rule%20in%20this%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mr%20Nedumpara%20kept%20speaking%2C%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20intervened%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20obstructing%20in%20the%20process%20of%20administration%20of%20justice!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20still%20did%20not%20back%20down.%20As%20he%20kept%20speaking%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20all%2C%20we%20will%20not%20hear%20you%20till%20you%20follow%20the%20procedure%20prescribed.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nedumpara%20said%20they%20will%20be%20filing%20an%20application%20and%20that%20they%20boarded%20a%20night%20flight%20to%20reach%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BBe%20kind%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20budge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20refused%20to%20hear%20arguments%20by%20Senior%20Advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20president%20Adish%20Agarwalla%2C%20who%20wanted%20to%20intervene%20during%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20reminded%20the%20lawyer%20of%20the%20contempt%20of%20court%20action%20he%20has%20faced%20in%20the%20past.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20Mr%20Nedumpara%20guilty%20of%20contempt.%20He%20had%20then%20given%20an%20undertaking%20that%20he%20will%20never%20again%20%26quot%3Battempt%20to%20browbeat%20any%20Judge%20either%20of%20this%20Court%20or%20of%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%26quot%3B.%20The%20court%20sentenced%20him%20to%20three%20months%20imprisonment%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%2C%20however%2C%20suspended%20only%20if%20Shri%20Nedumpara%20continues%20in%20future%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20undertaking%20given%20to%20us%20today%26quot%3B.%20He%20was%20also%20barred%20from%20practising%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20SBI%20to%20disclose%20all%20details%2C%20including%20the%20alphanumeric%20number%20and%20serial%20number%2C%20if%20any%2C%20of%20the%20bonds%20redeemed.%20It%20also%20asked%20the%20SBI%20chairman%20to%20submit%20an%20affidavit%2C%20stating%20that%20no%20info%20has%20been%20withheld.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20was%20asked%20to%20upload%20the%20data%20received%20from%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710758220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5lad5pdg_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_18_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-supreme-court-dont-shout-at-me-chief-justice-thunders-at-lawyer-in-poll-bonds-hearing-5261571%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20witnessed%20drama