w-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-rejects-adani-firm-s-plea-for-over-rs-1-300-cr-as-lps-from-raj-discom-124031800510_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsc-rejects-adani-firm-s-plea-for-over-rs-1-300-cr-as-lps-from-raj-discom-124031800510_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dell's%20Shocking%20Memo%3A%20No%20Promotion%20For%20Employees%20Preferring%20Work%20From%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDell%2C%20a%20prominent%20laptop%20brand%2C%20is%20facing%20flak%20after%20it%20recently%20announced%20a%20policy%20change%20regarding%20promotions%20for%20remote%20workers.%20In%20a%20memo%20circulated%20in%20February%2C%20Dell%20informed%20its%20remote%20employees%20that%20while%20they%20can%20continue%20working%20from%20home%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20eligible%20for%20promotions%20or%20allowed%20to%20change%20roles%20within%20the%20company%2C%C2%A0%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Ftech%2Fnews%2Fdell-workers-can-stay-remote-but-theyre-not-going-to-get-promoted%2Farticleshow%2F108564894.cms%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%2C%C2%A0accessed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%C2%A0informed%20its%20employees%20of%20a%20return-to-office%20mandate%20and%20also%20said%20they%20would%20be%20categorised%20as%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bremote%26quot%3B%20workers.%20As%20per%20the%20memo%2C%20hybrid%20employees%20are%20required%20to%20spend%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20an%20approved%20office.%20Meanwhile%2C%20employees%20who%20prefer%20to%20continue%20working%20remotely%20have%20the%20option%20to%20transition%20to%20full-time%20remote%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20this%20choice%2C%20the%20fully%20remote%20workers%20will%20not%20be%20eligible%20for%20promotions%20or%20can%20switch%20roles%20within%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20remote%20team%20members%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20the%20trade-offs%3A%20Career%20advancement%2C%20including%20applying%20to%20new%20roles%20in%20the%20company%2C%20will%20require%20a%20team%20member%20to%20reclassify%20as%20hybrid%20onsite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Dell%20had%20a%20hybrid%20work%20culture%20long%20before%20COVID-19%20struck.%C2%A0However%2C%20now%20the%20company's%20strict%20return-to-office%20(RTO)%20policies%2C%20have%20left%20employees%20shocked%20and%20disheartened.%20Several%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20working%20remotely%20for%20years%2C%20said%20they%20are%20worried%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20move%20up%20in%20their%20jobs%20or%20have%20the%20same%20flexibility%20they%20had%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDell%20cared%20about%20the%20work%2C%20not%20the%20location.%20I%20would%20say%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20every%20team%20was%20remote%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20employee%20at%20Dell%20who's%20worked%20remotely%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fem%3E%20last%20month.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20said%2C%20''The%20new%20policy%20is%20deeply%20disheartening.%20Many%20of%20us%20have%20been%20successfully%20working%20remotely%20for%20years%2C%20delivering%20quality%20results.%20It%20feels%20like%20our%20dedication%20and%20hard%20work%20are%20being%20overlooked.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''It's%20demotivating%20to%20learn%20that%20our%20contributions%20may%20not%20be%20recognized%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20those%20working%20in%20office.%20This%20decision%20undermines%20the%20value%20of%20remote%20work%20and%20disregards%20the%20achievements%20of%20remote%20employees.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710758040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F202