%25%20of%20children%20in%20the%20anganwadi%20centres.%20The%20anganwadi%20workers%20who%20provide%20nutritional%20support%20to%20children%20measure%20the%20weight%20and%20height%20of%20children%20in%20their%20respective%20centre%20for%20the%20Poshan%20Tracker%20which%20is%20a%20public%20dashboard%20comprising%20of%20monthly%20data%20from%20all%20the%20states%2C%20the%20report%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Poshan%20Tracker%2C%2039%25%20of%20around%2083%20million%20children%20in%20the%20anganwadi%20centres%20in%20September%202023%20had%20experienced%20stunting%20which%20was%201.8%20percentage%20points%20lower%20than%20the%20NFHS%20data.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Poshan%20Tracker%20data%20showed%20that%2018%25%20children%20were%20underweight%20which%20was%2013.7%20%25%20lower%20than%20NFHS%20data%20and%20wasting%20prevalence%20was%206%25%20which%20was%2012.1%20percentage%20points%20lower%20than%20in%20the%20NFHS%20data%2C%20researchers%20Lindsay%20Jaacks%2C%20Ananya%20Awasthi%20and%20Apoorva%20Kalra%20wrote%20in%20their%20commentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jaacks%20is%20a%20professor%20and%20chair%20of%20global%20health%20and%20nutrition%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Edinburgh.%20Awasthi%20and%20Kalra%20are%20at%20Anuvaad%20Solutions%2C%20a%20non-profit%20in%20India%20working%20on%20health%20and%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20underlined%20that%20these%20discrepancies%20might%20be%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20Poshan%20Tracker%20captures%20data%20from%20children%20in%20anganwadis%20and%20presents%20the%20true%20picture%20of%20undernutrition%20prevalent%20in%202023%20while%20the%20NFHS%202019-21%20has%20the%20older%20data.%20Further%2C%20the%20researchers%20noted%20that%20real-time-community%20monitoring%20using%20Poshan%20Tracker%20might%20have%20only%20resulted%20in%20improved%20delivery%20of%20nutrition%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710757836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F06160416%2FDFID-photo.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fdata-mismatch-poshan-estimates-lower-prevalence-of-undernutrition-compared-to-nfhs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Poshan%20Tracker%20data%20showed%20that%2018%25%20children%20were%20underweight%20which%20was%2013.7%20%25%20lower%20than%20NFHS%20data%2C%20as%20per%20a%20commentary%20published%20in%20The%20Lancet%20Regional%20Health%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20a%20peer-reviewed%20medical%20journal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fdata-mismatch-poshan-estimates-lower-prevalence-of-undernutrition-compared-to-nfhs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sara%20Ali%20Khan%20raises%20the%20bar%20with%20her%20latest%20look%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710757800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108551929%2Cimgsize-100556.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fsara-ali-khan-raises-the-fashion-bar-with-her-latest-look-in-an-exquisite-floral-gown%2Fphotostory%2F108551929.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108551929.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESara%20Ali%20Khan%20sets%20fashion%20goals%20in%20intricate%20floral%20embroidery%20adorned%20gown.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fsara-ali-khan-raises-the-fashion-bar-with-her-latest-look-in-an-exquisite-floral-gown%2Fphotostory%2F108551929.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Ex