industantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fcbi-allows-to-set-up-medical-board-to-examine-avinash-bhosale-101706384538894.html%5C%22%3Ealleged%20involvement%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Yes%20Bank-Dewan%20Housing%20Finance%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(DHFL)%20loan%20fraud%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20top%20donor%20to%20the%20party%2C%20according%20to%20the%20list%20is%20Cyrus%20Poonawalla%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Poonawalla%20group%20that%20privately%20owns%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India.%20Poonawalla%20has%20donated%20a%20total%20Rs%203.75%20crore%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20NCP%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-demands-bharat-ratna-for-serum-institute-founder-cyrus-poonawalla-5058096%5C%22%3Edemanded%20Bharat%20Ratna%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Poonawalla%20and%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20Serum%20Institute%E2%80%99s%20vaccine%20has%20proved%20effective%20for%20many%20diseases%2C%20including%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20received%20electoral%20bonds%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20from%20Modern%20Road%20Makers%20Pvt%20and%20Rs%202%20crore%20each%20from%20United%20Shippers%20Ltd%20and%20Bharti%20Airtel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20received%20Rs%201%20crore%20each%20from%20Oberoi%20Realty%2C%20Abhay%20Firodia%20and%20Bhansali%20Emam.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20has%20received%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20each%20from%20Vivek%20Jadhav%20and%20United%20Phosphorus%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20submission%20stated%20that%20it%20is%20unable%20to%20provide%20detailed%20particulars%20of%20each%20donor%20as%20it%20had%20not%20maintained%20such%20records%20as%20they%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20not%20expected%E2%80%9D%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20unable%20to%20furnish%20detailed%20particulars%20of%20donors%20against%20each%20bond%20as%20we%20neither%20maintained%20complete%20details%20of%20the%20same%20nor%20issued%20any%20receipts%20against%20the%20Bonds%20received%20as%20initially%20we%20were%20not%20expected%20to%20maintain%20any%20details%20of%20electoral%20bearer%20bonds%20As%20well%20as%20during%20the%20election%20period%20there%20is%20movement%20of%20office%20bearers%20for%20campaign.%20Wherever%20possible%20we%20have%20indicated%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person%20through%20whom%20bonds%20were%20received%20by%20the%20Party%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20mandated%20data%20published%20by%20the%20EC%20last%20week%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20Parliament%20received%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2050%20crores%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20Maharashtra%20Pradesh%20received%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20between%20April%2012%2C%202019%20and%20February%2015%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%20is%20among%20the%20ten%20political%20parties%20that%20have%20disclosed%20their%20donors%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20top%20three%20recipients%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20have%20not%20yet%20disclosed%20the%20names%20of%20their%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthree-left-parties-declared-to-ec-that-they-dont-accept-electoral-bonds%5C%22%3EThree%20Left%20parties%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%2C%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist-Leninist)%20Liberation%20%E2%80%93%20told%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20their%20submissions%20in%202023%20that%20they%20have%20not%20received%20any%20money%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710756938000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F18153955%2FFt6I46YakAEFJmT.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbajaj-finserv-cyrus-poonawalla-top-donors-ncp-2019-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20list%20of%20donors%20made%20available%20by%20NCP%2C%20it%20has%20received%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2037.75%20crore%20between%20January%202019%20and%20May%202019.%20Bajaj%20Finserv%20donated%20Rs%207.5%20crore%20during%20this%20period%2C%20and%20Poonawalla%20donated%20Rs%203.75%20crore%20to%20the%20party.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbajaj-finserv-cyrus-poonawalla-top-donors-ncp-2019-polls%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zoho%20CEO%20On%20FIITJEE%20Ad%3A%20%26quot%3BIntense%20Pressure%20Creates%20Zombified%20Adults%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EZoho%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Sridhar%20Vembu%20reacted%20to%20FIITJEE's%20latest%20advertisement%20which%20drew%20heavy%20criticism%20for%20its%20unethical%20tactics.%20The%20print%20ad%20used%20a%20student's%20image%20to%20suggest%20declining%20performance%20after%20leaving%20their%20institute.%20It%20further%20stooped%20to%20fear-mongering%20by%20associating%20a%20competitor%20with%20student%20suicides%20and%20using%20inflammatory%20language%20like%20%26quot%3Bevil.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vembu%20reposted%20the%20ad%20and%20said%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bultra-competitive%20exam%20pressure%26quot%3B%20on%20students%20and%20young%20adults.%20He%20added%20that%20his%20company%20has%20%26quot%3Bpledged%20to%20not%20even%20consider%20academic%20credentials%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20to%20get%20out%20of%20this%20ultra-competitive%20exam%20pressure%20on%20children%20and%20young%20adults.%20This%20is%20one%20area%20where%20I%20would%20*not*%20learn%20from%20East%20Asia%20but%20instead%20learn%20from%20Finland%20which%20has%20a%20superb%20state-funded%20educational%20system%20that%20serves%20every%20child%20without%20such%20competitive%20insanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vembu%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIndia%20has%20to%20get%20out%20of%20this%20ultra-competitive%20exam%20pressure%20on%20children%20and%20young%20adults.%20This%20is%20one%20area%20where%20I%20would%20*not*%20learn%20from%20East%20Asia%20but%20instead%20learn%20from%20Finland%20which%20has%20a%20superb%20state-funded%20educational%20system%20that%20serves%20every%20child%20without%20such%20competitive%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAjdkIl0Nmt%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAjdkIl0Nmt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sridhar%20Vembu%20(%40svembu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsvembu%2Fstatus%2F1769309567584977162%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zoho%20Chief%20slammed%20the%20competitive%20exam%20culture%20and%20said%20that%20pressure%20at%20a%20young%20age%20%26quot%3Bdestroys%20talent%20and%20creates%20zombified%20adults.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20rat%20race%20to%20extinction.%20Intense%20competition%20is%20for%20companies%20serving%20a%20market%20and%20for%20sports%2C%20not%20for%20children%20in%20education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20an%20employer%2C%20we%20have%20pledged%20to%20not%20even%20consider%20academic%20credentials.%20We%20are%20also%20investing%20in%20educational%20alternatives%20that%20are%20inspired%20by%20Finland.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%20over%20two%20lakh%20views%20and%20three%20thousand%20likes.%20Several%20people%20also%20took%20to%20the%20comments%20section%20to%20share%20their%20views%20on%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20important%20thing%20to%20learn%20from%20Finland%20is%20the%