0other%20states%2C%20but%20has%20now%20spread%20west%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F17%2Fus-news%2Fexperts-warn-deadly-threat-to-pets-is-sweeping-across-the-united-states%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20outlet%20further%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20flatworms%20cause%20schistosomiasis%20in%20dogs%2C%20which%20can%20be%20fatal.%20The%20parasite%20is%20contracted%20when%20dogs%20wade%20or%20swim%20in%20freshwater%20where%20infected%20snails%20are%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDogs%20can%20die%20from%20this%20infection%2C%20so%20we%20are%20hoping%20to%20raise%20public%20awareness%20that%20it's%20there.%20If%20you're%20swimming%20in%20the%20Colorado%20River%20with%20them%2C%20your%20pets%20are%20in%20peril%2C%26quot%3B%20UC%20Riverside%20nematology%20professor%20Adler%20Dillman%20told%20the%20UC%20Riverside%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20tested%202%2C000%20snails%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Colorado%20River%20between%20March%20and%20August%202023%20after%20finding%20out%20several%20dogs%20infected%20by%20parasite%20had%20gone%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20said%20their%20findings%20suggest%20%26quot%3Ba%20wider%20distribution%20of%20the%20parasite%20than%20previously%20reported.%20Our%20findings%20have%20implications%20for%20public%20health%2C%20veterinary%20medicine%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20conservation%2C%20contributing%20to%20developing%20effective%20control%20strategies%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20this%20emerging%20infectious%20disease%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20significant%20finding%20marks%20the%20westernmost%20record%20of%20this%20endemic%20North%20American%20schistosome%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20identification%20of%20the%20parasite%20in%20an%20area%20with%20a%20documented%20history%20of%20canine%20schistosomiasis%20emphasises%20the%20persistence%20and%20potential%20expansion%20of%20this%20parasitic%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3