en%20steadily%20spreading%20its%20poisonous%20tentacles%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20consolidated%20itself%20and%20its%20rule.%E2%80%9D%20For%20this%20he%20explicitly%20blames%20the%20BJP%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20one%20quality%20Indians%20cannot%20be%20accused%20of%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20sensitive%2C%20and%20the%20higher%20up%20the%20pecking%20order%20or%20social%20ladder%20one%20is%2C%20the%20more%20insensitive%20one%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20his%20point%2C%20he%20says%20that%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbareilly%2Fman-jailed-for-wrapping-food-in-newspaper-with-pics-of-hindu-deities-in-up%2Farticleshow%2F92661702.cms%5C%22%3Etake%20offence%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20a%20man%20in%20UP%20wraps%20non-vegetarian%20food%20in%20a%20newspaper%20containing%20pictures%20of%20Hindu%20Gods%2C%20or%20when%20a%20person%20in%20Assam%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fassam-man-dressed-up-as-lord-shiva-arrested-after-street-play-released-on-bail%2Farticleshow%2F92789831.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Edresses%20up%20as%20Shiva%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20street%20play%20protesting%20against%20inflation%2C%20or%20when%20bail%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkissi-se-na-kehna-mohammed-zubair-arrested-for-tweeting-photo-from-1983-hindi-film%5C%22%3Eis%20rejected%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20tweeting%20a%20photograph%20from%20a%201983%20film%20by%20a%20renowned%20director%2C%20or%20when%20an%20MP%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fkali-is-meat-eating-alcohol-accepting-goddess-mahua-moitra-views-personal-says-tmc%2Farticleshow%2F92683103.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20is%20harassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20saying%20her%20Goddess%20eats%20meat%20and%20drinks%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20ab