2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-news-one-nation-one-election-explained-what-is-it-how-can-it-work-5236599%5C%22%3ESimultaneous%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20in%20the%20news%20again%20with%20the%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20ex-President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-nath-kovind-led-panel-submits-report-on-1-nation-1-poll-to-president-5235822%5C%22%3Esubmitting%20its%20final%20recommendations%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20current%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-panel-gets-21-000-suggestions-81-affirm-idea-4906526%5C%22%3Ecommission%20has%20recommended%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20must%20develop%20a%20legally%20tenable%20mechanism%20to%20restore%20the%20cycle%20of%20simultaneous%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20maintained%20that%20the%20rationale%20for%20considering%20simultaneous%20elections%20is%20that%20it%20would%20reduce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%5C%22%3Eelection-time%20expenses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20time%20and%20energy.%20But%20the%20opposition%2C%20led%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fentire-idea-must-be-abandoned-congress-chief-mallikarjun-kharge-on-one-nation-one-election-4892949%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sees%20this%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20nationalise%20state%20elections%20to%20benefit%20itself.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-will-damage-idea-of-parliamentary-democracy-aap-4898065%5C%22%3EThe%20parties%20fear%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20its%20pole%20position%20in%20national%20politics%2C%20will%20eventually%20overshadow%20regional%20players%20in%20state%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESimultaneous%20Polls%20In%20Recent%20Years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20saw%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%202014%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Sikkim%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20then%20again%20in%202019%20in%20all%20these%20but%20Telangana.%20Except%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20regional%20parties%20not%20only%20won%20the%20state%20election%20in%20the%20remaining%20four%20states%20but%20also%20went%20on%20to%20register%20maximum%20seats%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20of%20Telangana%20won%2053%25%20of%20assembly%20seats%20and%2065%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Telangana%20in%202014.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%20(YSRCP)%20won%2086%25%20of%20the%20assembly%20seats%20and%2088%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20In%20Odisha%2C%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20won%2080%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20elections%20and%2057%25%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20and%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20Sikkim%20Krantikari%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20won%2053%25%20of%20assembly%20seats%20and%20100%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20won%2068%25%20of%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20100%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20votes%2C%20we%20see%20identical%20vote%20shares%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20elections%20for%20the%20top%20three%20parties%20in%20these%20states%2C%20with%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20being%20in%20the%20%C2%B1%202.5%25%20range%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%20The%20trend%20held%20in%20Odisha%20too%2C%20but%20there%20the%20BJP%20registered%20a%20much%20higher%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20national%20elections%20(6%20percentage%20points%20more%20than%20its%20share%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls)%2C%20largely%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20others.%20The%20YSRCP%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Odisha%2C%20and%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20BJP-TDP%20combine%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20registered%20almost%20similar%20vote%20shares%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20their%20respective%20states%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20A%20similar%20trend%20is%20visible%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20got%20a%20slight%20boost%20in%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20table%20shows%20vote%20shares%20in%20both%20state%20and%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Feo57lib8_vote-share_625x300_18_March_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch6%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%20indiavotes.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh6%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absolute%20numbers%20of%20votes%20polled%20also%20show%20a%20similar%20pattern.%20The%20YSRCP%2C%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20got%20almost%20a%20similar%20number%20of%20votes%20in%20both%20the%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20same%20was%20the%20case%20for%20the%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(TRS%2C%20now%20rechristened%20BRS)%20and%20the%20BJP-TDP%20alliance%20in%20Telangana%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Odisha.%20Only%20the%20BJP%20got%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20votes%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Sikkim%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20due%20to%20the%20national%20character%20of%20the%20elections.%20Interestingly%2C%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20too%2C%20did%20better%20in%20the%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20table%20shows%20absolute%20number%20of%20votes%20polled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6sfibajo_table-2_625x300_18_March_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch6%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%20indiavotes.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh6%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20has%20been%20seeing%20simultaneous%20elections%20since%201999%2C%20whichever%20party%20wins%20the%20state%20elections%20goes%20on%20to%20win%20the%20maximum%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20too.%20Karnataka%20also%20witnessed%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%201999%20and%202004%2C%20and%20a%20similar%20trend%20was%20visible%20here%2C%20too.%20The%20Congress%20won%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20the%20state%20elections%20in%201999%20as%20well%20as%20the%20maximum%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20-%2018%20of%20the%20total%2028.%20Later%2C%20in%202004%2C%20the%20BJP%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20and%20also%20went%20on%20to%20win%2018%20of%20the%2028%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20of%20Simultaneous%20Polls%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20and%20national%20elections%20were%20held%20simultaneously%20in%20India%20from%201952%20to%201967.%20The%20Congress%20party%20ruled%20at%20the%20Centre%20as%20well%20as%20in%20a%20majority%20of%20states%2C%20except%20for%20intermittent%20periods%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Odisha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20got%20more%20than%20350%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%201952%2C%201957%20and%201962.%20This%20was%20because%20the%20party%20had%20stalwart%20leaders%20like%20Nehru%20not%20only%20at%20the%20national%20level%20but%20also%20in%20states.%20Morarji%20Desai%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Neelam%20Sanjeev%20Reddy%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Bidhan%20Chandra%20Roy%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Govind%20Ballabh%20Pant%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20K.%20Kamraj%20in%20Madras%2C%20Yashwant%20Rao%20Chavan%20Maharashtra%20and%20Krishna%20Singh%20in%20Bihar%20were%20a%20few%20such%20politicians.%20There%20was%20also%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20political%20competition%20to%20the%20Congress%20was%20much%20less%2C%20initially.%20The%20party's%20leadership%20helped%20it%20win%20state%20elections%20and%20also%20elect%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20parliamentarians%20from%20their%20respective%20states%20in%20national%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201952%20elections%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20percentages%20of%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20national%20and%20state%20elections%20were%20similar%20for%20the%20top%20five%20states%20-%20Bihar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bombay%2C%20Madras%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201967%20elections%20marked%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Congress's%20unchallenged%20supremacy.%20The%20party%20could%20not%20secure%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20eight%20of%20the%2016%20states%2C%20where%20non-Congress%20governments%20were%20installed.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20muster%20350-plus%20seats%2C%20and%20its%20tally%20dipped%20to%20283.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20parties%20and%20breakaway%20groups%20dented%20the%20grand%20old%20party's%20chances%20in%20many%20states%2C%20which%20was%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20It%20lost%20seats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Madras%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Kerala%20and%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Benefits%20From%20One%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%201967%20elections%20and%20the%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%20a%20few%20states%20in%202014%20and%202019%20show%20that%20strong%20regional%20parties%20tend%20to%20benefit%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20when%20polls%20are%20held%20together%2C%20because%20split-voting%2C%20that%20is%2C%20voting%20differently%20in%20state%20and%20national%20elections%2C%20is%20limited%20to%20urban%20centres.%20Voters%20choose%20different%20parties%20only%20when%20assembly%20and%20general%20elections%20are%20held%20at%20different%20times.%20The%20BJP's%20sweep%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%202019%20general%20polls%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20victory%20in%20state%20elections%20just%20a%20year%20later%20in%202020%2C%20underlines%20this.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20contrary%20to%20popular%20notion%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20not%20be%20the%20sole%20gainer%20in%20simultaneous%20elections.%20Strong%20regional%20parties%20stand%20to%20benefit%20too%20-%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20a%20surprise%20if%20they%20go%20on%20to%20win%20a%20few%20extra%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20as%20well%20in%20their%20respective%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710751800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2Fplepqar8_up-rally-ani-pic_650x400_30_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsimultaneous-polls-not-bjp-regional-parties-stand-to-gain-more-5261126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20results%20of%20the%201967%20elections%20and%20the%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%20a%20few%20states%20in%202014%20and%202019%20show%20that%20strong%20regional%20parties%20tend%20to%20benefit%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20when%20polls%20are%20held%2