he%20martial%20arts%20form%20Krav%20Maga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Badola%20chased%20the%20two%20snatchers%20and%20disarmed%20the%20one%20with%20the%20pistol%20after%20a%20violent%20exchange.%20The%20second%20accused%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20was%20able%20to%20escape.%20Mr%20Badola%20then%20called%20112%20and%20informed%20the%20PCR.%20He%20continued%20searching%20for%20the%20second%20accused%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20local%20police.%20The%20criminal%20tried%20to%20escape%20by%20blending%20in%20with%20the%20crowd%20and%20sitting%20near%20a%20fountain.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20located%20and%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDCP%20(New%20Delhi)%20Devesh%20Mahla%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fsnatchers-pick-wrong-guy-an-encounter-cop%2Farticleshow%2F108569736.cms%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%20(TOI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20two%20snatchers%20were%20identified%20as%20Gaurav%20and%20Pawan%20Dev%20Both%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20sections%20for%20robbery%20with%20intent%20to%20cause%20death.%20The%20police%20have%20collected%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20area%20and%20increased%20patrolling%20around%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EVinod%20Badola%20has%20led%20numerous%20high-profile%20missions.%20In%20October%202013%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20found%20gangster%20Nitu%20Dabodia%20and%20shot%20him%20in%20an%20encounter%20near%20a%20hotel%20in%20south%20Delhi's%20Vasant%20Kunj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20that%2C%20Mr%20Badola%20participated%20in%20other%20counterterrorism%20operations%2C%20one%20of%20which%20earned%20him%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister's%20Special%20Operations%20Medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Badola%20and%20his%20team%20unearthed%20a%20new%20method%20used%20by%20a%20Taliban-backed%20group%20to%20smuggle%20narcotics%20in%20India.%20They%20discovered%20that%20gang%20members%20were%20travelling%20by%20land%20from%20Afghanistan%20via%20Iran%20before%20sailing%20to%20ports%20in%20western%20India.%20Approximately%20330%20kilos%20of%20heroin%20valued%20at%20%E2%82%B91%2C320%20crore%20was%20found.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20this%20seizure%20was%20the%20biggest%20in%20Delhi%20Police's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710748980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1vf6ahds_delhi-encounter-specialist_625x300_18_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fchain-snatchers-target-delhi-police-encounter-specialist-this-happens-next-5260757%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20arrested%20two%20chain%20snatchers%2C%20who%20targeted%20a%20jogger%20at%20Nehru%20Park%20in%20the%20Chanakyapuri%20area%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fchain-snatchers-target-delhi-police-encounter-specialist-this-happens-next-5260757%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fchain-snatchers-target-delhi-police-encounter-specialist-this-happens-next-5260757%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fchain-snatchers-target-delhi-police-encounter-specialist-this-happens-next-5260757%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Governor%20Resigns%2C%20May%20Contest%20Elections%20From%20Tamil%20Nadu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18131812%2FTS-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Telangana%20governor%20and%20Puducherry%20lieutenant%20governor%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20has%20resigned%20from%20her%20dual%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Raj%20Bhavan%20press%20communique%20here%20said%20she%20sent%20in%20her%20resignation%20to