0get%20clarifications%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20Bills%20were%20still%20pending%20in%20her%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20held%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20court%20orders%20after%20the%20government%20confined%20the%20occasion%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20official%20bungalow%20citing%20COVID-19%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20withdrew%20protocol%20honours%20to%20her%20when%20she%20left%20the%20state.%20Neither%20the%20collectors%20nor%20superintendents%20of%20police%20received%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20did%20not%20clear%20the%20traffic%20congestion%20on%20roads%20when%20she%20travelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20sent%20in%20his%20resignation%20to%20Soundararajan%20after%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20the%20November%202023%20assembly%20election%20through%20his%20officer%20on%20special%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710748263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18131812%2FTS-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-governor-resigns-may-contest-elections-from-tamil-nadu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20also%20resigned%20as%20Puducherry%20lieutenant%20governor.%20Her%20term%20as%20Telangana%20governor%20was%20marked%20by%20a%20running%20feud%20with%20former%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-governor-resigns-may-contest-elections-from-tamil-nadu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taliban%20says%20eight%20killed%20in%20Pakistan's%20two%20air%20strikes%20in%20Afghanistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710747682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108581798%2Cimgsize-504490.cms%22%2C%22origi