atment%20on%20an%20energy%20project%2C%20according%20to%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter.%20The%20probe%2C%20which%20is%20also%20looking%20at%20Indian%20renewable%20energy%20company%20Azure%20Power%20Global%20Ltd.%2C%20is%20being%20handled%20by%20the%20US%20Attorney%E2%80%99s%20Office%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20and%20the%20Justice%20Department%E2%80%99s%20fraud%20unit%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20was%20contacted%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20for%20a%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20investigation%20against%20our%20chairman%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adani%20Group%20said%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20business%20group%20that%20operates%20with%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20governance%2C%20we%20are%20subject%20to%20and%20fully%20compliant%20with%20anti-corruption%20and%20anti-bribery%20laws%20in%20India%20and%20other%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeclines%20in%20share%20values%20of%20several%20of%20Adani%20companies%20have%20been%20seen%20and%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20correlates%20it%20with%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-15%2Fus-prosecutors-widen-investigation-into-adani-group-focus-on-potential-bribery%5C%22%3Enews%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cthat%20US%20prosecutors%20have%20widened%20their%20probe%20of%20the%20port-to-power%20conglomerate%20to%20focus%20on%20whether%20it%20may%20have%20engaged%20in%20bribery.%E2%80%9D%20Most%20of%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20shares%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20has%20a%20massive%20corporate%20footprint%20in%20India%2C%20with%20ports%2C%20airports%2C%20power%20lines%20and%20highway%20contracts.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20attracts%20capital%20globally.%20The%20Hindenburg%20report%20by%20a%20short-seller%20Research%20body%20based%20in%20the%20US%20in%20January%20last%20year%20raised%20serious%20issues%20ab