o%20account%20the%20assurance%20of%20the%20Solicitor%20General%2C%20we%20direct%20SEBI%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%20in%20the%20other%20two%20cases%20preferably%20within%20three%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20its%20report%20emphasised%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20US%20law%20allows%20federal%20prosecutors%20to%20pursue%20foreign%20corruption%20allegations%20if%20they%20involve%20certain%20links%20to%20American%20investors%20or%20markets.%E2%80%9D%20It%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CGautam%20Adani%2C%20his%20company%20and%20Azure%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20charged%20with%20wrongdoing%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%2C%20and%20investigations%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20lead%20to%20prosecutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710745235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17154946%2Fimage-1516.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-entity-under-investigation-in-the-us-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bloomberg%20reports%20that%20an%20Adani%20entity%2C%20%E2%80%9Cor%20people%20linked%20to%20the%20company%20including%20Gautam%20Adani%20are%20being%20investigated%E2%80%9D%20if%20they%20may%20have%20bribed%20Indian%20officials.%20Adani%20Group%20says%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20aware%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-entity-under-investigation-in-the-us-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kristen%20Wiig%E2%80%99s%201960s-Set%20%E2%80%98Palm%20Royale%E2%80%99%20Is%20Unserious%20In%20All%20the%20Best%20Ways%3A%20TV%20Review%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710745200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPalm_Royale_Photo_010102.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235939481%22%2