he%20bonds%20purchased.%20In%20order%20to%20avoid%20any%20controversy%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20bank%20should%20file%20an%20affidavit%20by%205%20pm%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20has%20disclosed%20all%20details%20in%20its%20custody%20and%20that%20no%20details%20have%20been%20withheld%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20SBI%2C%20said%20that%20the%20bank%20was%20happy%20to%20furnish%20whatever%20details%20the%20court%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20judgment%2C%20we%20had%20expressed%20asked%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20disclose%20%E2%80%98all%20details.%E2%80%99%20That%20includes%20the%20bond%20numbers%20as%20well.%20The%20bank%20cannot%20be%20selective%20in%20disclosing%20all%20details.%20Do%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20orders%20of%20this%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-uploads-electoral-bonds-data%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20information%20released%20by%20the%20SBI%20and%20EC%20on%20directives%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20week%20did%20not%20contain%20key%20details%20that%20would%20help%20trace%20which%20businesses%20and%20individuals%20were%20paying%20which%20parties.%20This%20meant%20that%20details%20of%20possible%20quid%20pro%20quo%20arrangements%20are%20still%20not%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20an%20industry%20body%20%E2%80%93%20ASSOCHAM%20%E2%80%93%20reportedly%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20public%20disclosure%20of%20the%20unique%20numbers%20associated%20with%20electoral%20bonds.%20Senior%20advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20tried%20to%20intervene%20in%20court%20on%20Monday%20and%20speak%20for%20FICCI%20and%20ASSOCHAM%2C%20but%20the%20chief%20justice%20intervened%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20such%20application%20on%20board.%E2%80%9D%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710742714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-orders-sbi-to-release-unique-codes-links-to-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20manner%20of%20doubt%20that%20the%20SBI%20is%20required%20to%20furnish%20all%20details%20available%20with%20it.%20This%2C%20we%20clarify%2C%20will%20include%20the%20alphanumeric%20number%20and%20serial%20number%2C%20if%20any%2C%20of%20the%20bonds%20purchased%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-orders-sbi-to-release-unique-codes-links-to-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CAG's%202017%20Report%20Flagged%20Serious%20Irregularities%20by%20Future%20Gaming%2C%20Top%20Purchaser%20of%20Electoral%20Bonds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18113856%2Fimage-1973.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Comptroller%20and%20Audit%20General%20of%20India%20(CAG)%20flagged%20serious%20irregularities%20by%20marketing%20agents%2C%20including%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20owned%20by%20lottery%20king%20Santiago%20Martin%2C%20in%20a%202017%20report%20submitted%20to%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcags-2017-report-pointed-out-serious-irregularities-by-martin%2Famp_articleshow%2F108569003.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20buyers%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%2C%20was%20highlighted%20in%20recent%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20audit%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20in%202015%20following%20complaints%20of%20corruption%20and%20violations%20in%20lotteries%2C%20with%20Martin%20being%20a%20major%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20marketing%20agents%20(MA)%20have%20cornered%2098.60%25%20of%20sale%20proceeds%20of%20lotteries%20while%20the%20state%20could%20receive%20a%20meagre%201.40%25%20of%20sale%20proceeds%2C%20during%20the%20audit%20period%202010-2016%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20CAG%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Performance%20Audit%20on%20Sikkim%20State%20Lotteries%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20CAG%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20award%20of%20marketing%20contract%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20lotteries%20to%20various%20lottery%20MAs%20was%20characterised%20by%20lack%20of%20transparency%2C%20frequent%20extensions%20of%20contract%20without%20competitive%20bidding%20and%20considerable%20delay%20in%20finalisation%20of%20tenders%20that%20led%20to%20huge%20loss%20of%20revenue%20to%20the%20state.%20The%20operations%20of%20lottery%20business%20were%20fully%20controlled%20and%20conducted%20by%20the%20private%20operators%20called%20MA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Sikkim%2C%20Martin%20operated%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Nagaland%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20lottery%20scams%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20reported%20citing%20officials%20familiar%20with%20his%20dealings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20ministry%20issued%20directions%20to%20state%20governments%20to%20oversee%20lottery%20marketing%20arrangements%20and%20%E2%80%9Censure%20that%20the%20persons%2C%20firms%20involved%20in%20selling%2C%20distribution%2C%20printing%20of%20lotteries%20do%20not%20violate%20any%20provision%20of%20the%20Act%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMartin%E2%80%99s%20lottery%20empire%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20he%20is%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20industries%20such%20as%20real%20estate%2C%20media%2C%20construction%2C%20software%2C%20and%20pharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20emerged%20as%20the%20biggest%20buyer%20of%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20company%20spent%20Rs%201%2C368%20crore%20on%20them%20between%20October%202020%20and%20January%202024%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1065321%2F77-of-dmks-electoral-bond-money-came-from-lottery-king-santiago-martin%5C%22%3EProject%20Electoral%20Bond%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20investigative%20collaboration%20project%20involving%20three%20news%20organisations%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20Newslaundry%2C%20Scroll%2C%20The%20News%20Minute%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20several%20independent%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20received%20Rs%20656.5%20crore%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20April%202019%20and%20November%202023%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20citing%20details%20filed%20by%20the%20party%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20this%2C%20Rs%20509%20crore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdmk-got-at-least-rs-504-crore-from-future-gaming-group-in-electoral-bonds-ec-data-reveals%5C%22%3Ewas%20donated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Martin%2C%20according%20to%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20unclear%20to%20whom%20the%20company%20donated%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20investigative%20report%20found%20that%20several%20companies%20which%20donated%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20political%20parties%20faced%20raids%20several%20times%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20And%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20was%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMartin%20has%20been%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20agencies%20since%202007.%20In%202011%2C%20the%20CBI%20registered%2030%20cases%20against%20him%20and%20his%20close%20aides%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20launched%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20against%20Martin.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20agency%20attached%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20assets%20from%20April%202022%20to%20May%202023.%20Between%20April%20and%20December%202022%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20290%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRaids%20were%20also%20conducted%20on%20properties%20owned%20by%20Martin%20and%20his%20son-in-law%2C%20Aadhav%20Arjun%2C%20in%20September%202022%20and%20April%202023.%20In%20this%20period%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20bought%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%20303%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710742407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F18113856%2Fimage-1973.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcags-2017-report-flagged-serious-irregularities-by-future-gaming-top-purchaser-of-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20to%20audit%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20in%202015%20following%20complaints%20of%20corruption%20and%20violations%20in%20lotteries%2C%20with%20owner%20Santiago%20Martin%20being%20a%20major%20player.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcags-2017-report-flagged-serious-irregularities-by-future-gaming-top-purchaser-of-electoral-bonds%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20meets%20New%20Zealand%20counter