st%20differs%20slightly%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull%20English%26quot%3B%20in%20that%20traditional%20Irish%20breakfasts%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ealways%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Einclude%20black%20or%20white%20pudding%20and%20are%20often%20served%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fina-gartens-irish-soda-bread-recipe-review-st-patricks-day-2022-3%5C%22%3Esoda%20bread%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20addition%20to%20regular%20toast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20products%20I%20used%20in%20this%20breakfast%20came%20from%20the%20specialty%20British%20food%20shop%20Myers%20of%20Keswick%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20founded%20in%201985.%20While%20British%20and%20Irish%20shops%20can%20be%20rare%20finds%2C%20even%20in%20major%20cities%20like%20New%20York%2C%20they%20offer%20international%20visitors%20an%20authentic%20taste%20of%20home%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20have%20come%20close%20to%20making%20a%20traditional%20Irish%20breakfast%20without%20this%20store.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20I%20made%20a%20traditional%20Irish%20breakfast%2C%20and%20how%20you%20can%2C%20too%2C%20this%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20snag%20some%20real%20Irish%20bacon%20and%20bangers%20from%20a%20specialty%20food%20shop%20in%20Manhattan.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22myers%20of%20keswick%20in%20the%20west%20village%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622bb521843ef30018e6ba70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20visited%20Myers%20of%20Keswick%2C%20a%20specialty%20food%20store%20in%20the%20West%20Village.%3Cp%3ERob%20Kim%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20could%20have%20stuck%20with%20American%20breakfast%20sausages%20and%20bacon%2C%20and%20nixed%20the%20white%20or%20black%20pudding%20altogether%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20my%20breakfast%20to%20be%20as%20traditional%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMyers%20of%20Keswick%20in%20the%20West%20Village%20had%20everything%20I%20needed%20for%20my%20breakfast%3A%20sausages%2C%20Irish%20bacon%2C%20white%20pudding%2C%20and%20even%20HP%20sauce%2C%20which%20is%20technically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-british-foods-that-foreigners-find-gross-2016-9%5C%22%3Ea%20British%20favorite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20add%20it%20anyway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20live%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20you%20can%20also%20order%20many%20types%20of%20British%20and%20Irish%20meat%20online%20at%20retailers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjollyposhfoods.com%2F%5C%22%3EJolly%20Posh%20Foods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20also%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20some%20white%20pudding%2C%20which%20was%20even%20made%20in%20Ireland.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22irish%20white%20pudding%20sausage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7a18f97ab0018751e26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIrish%20white%20pudding%20sausage.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20pudding%20usually%20consists%20of%20oats%2C%20pork%20meat%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20bread%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seasonings%2C%20while%20black%20pudding%20also%20contains%20pork%20or%20beef%20blood%20and%20is%20known%20as%20blood%20sausage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-british-foods-that-foreigners-find-gross-2016-9%5C%22%3Enot%20sound%20appetizing%20to%20some%20Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20grew%20up%20eating%20and%20loving%20the%20stuff.%20It's%20perfectly%20salty%2C%20fatty%2C%20and%20is%20often%20hard%20to%20find%20anywhere%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20bought%20some%20Irish%20soda%20bread.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22irish%20soda%20bread%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7b729e90c0019089068%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIrish%20soda%20bread.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20usually%20difficult%20to%20find%20soda%20bread%20in%20stores.%20However%2C%20since%20I%20prepared%20my%20breakfast%20around%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20some%20Irish-style%20soda%20bread%20in%20my%20local%20Wegmans%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBack%20in%20my%20kitchen%2C%20I%20started%20by%20chopping%20mushrooms%20and%20tomatoes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chopped%20tomatoes%20and%20mushrooms%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba77829e90c0019089031%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChopped%20mushrooms%20and%20tomatoes.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20quartered%20the%20tomatoes%20and%20thinly%20sliced%20the%20mushrooms%20before%20adding%20them%20to%20a%20skillet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20added%20about%20a%20tablespoon%20of%20Irish%20butter%20to%20the%20skillet%20and%20let%20the%20mushrooms%20cook%20slightly%20down%20before%20adding%20the%20tomatoes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mushrooms%20in%20a%20pan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba78029e90c0019089035%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMushrooms%20in%20a%20pan.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20use%20olive%20oil%20or%20any%20butter%20you%20have%20on%20hand%2C%20but%20using%20Irish%20butter%20like%20Kerry%20Gold%20will%20add%20a%20lot%20of%20flavor%20to%20the%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20then%20