97ab0018751e16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIrish%20bacon%20in%20a%20skillet.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBacon%20in%20the%20British%20Isles%20looks%20noticeably%20different%20compared%20to%20most%20standard%20bacon%20you'll%20find%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20In%20Ireland%2C%20bacon%20typically%20comes%20from%20the%20back%2C%20or%20the%20loin%2C%20of%20the%20pig%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20belly.%20It%20more%20closely%20resembles%20what%20we%20know%20as%20Canadian%20bacon%20or%20%26quot%3Bcountry%20ham%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20South.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENext%20up%2C%20I%20made%20the%20baked%20beans%2C%20which%20I%20expected%20to%20be%20my%20least%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20breakfast.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22baked%20beans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7c18f97ab0018751e69%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBaked%20beans.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20baked%20beans%20are%20super%20easy%20to%20make%20%E2%80%94%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20pour%20the%20can%20into%20a%20bowl%20or%20saucepan%20and%20heat%20them%20up%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20eat%20by%20this%20point%20and%20was%20dreading%20making%20yet%20another%20ingredient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20remembered%20not%20being%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20baked%20beans%20when%20I%20ate%20this%20meal%20as%20a%20child.%20Still%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20them%20a%20fair%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20about%2030%20minutes%20of%20cooking%2C%20my%20sausages%20were%20crispy%20and%20ready%20to%20eat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cooked%20sausages%20and%20white%20pudding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7c829e90c001908909e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECooked%20sausages%20and%20white%20pudding.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20immediately%20that%20I%20had%20made%20way%20too%20much%20food%2C%20but%20thankfully%20I%20had%20two%20roommates%20who%20were%20also%20dying%20to%20partake%20in%20the%20traditional%20breakfast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meal%20admittedly%20took%20quite%20a%20while%20and%20four%20different%20pans%20to%20make.%20I%20usually%20stick%20to%20yogurt%20and%20honey%20for%20breakfast%2C%20so%20this%20felt%20like%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ea%20lot%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20decided%20brown%20sauce%20was%20a%20necessity%20for%20my%20plate.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hp%20sauce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7d08f97ab0018751e70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHP%20Sauce.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHP%20Sauce%2C%20which%20tastes%20tangy%20and%20vinegary%2C%20is%20typically%20added%20to%20English%20breakfasts%2C%20but%20I%20grew%20up%20always%20adding%20it%20to%20the%20breakfasts%20at%20my%20grandparents'%20house%2C%20so%20I%20figured%20it%20would%20be%20alright.%20In%20Ireland%2C%20a%20similar%20brown%20sauce%20by%20Chef%20is%20also%20used%20for%20breakfasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20I%20assembled%20everything%20on%20my%20plate%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20at%20how%20delicious%20and%20authentic%20my%20breakfast%20looked.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22irish%20breakfast%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7da29e90c00190890b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20finished%20Irish%20breakfast.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20looked%20just%20like%20the%20Irish%20breakfast%20recipe%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.happyfoodstube.com%2Ffull-irish-breakfast%2F%5C%22%3EHappy%20Foods%20Tube%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20was%20following.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sausages%20had%20the%20perfect%20amount%20of%20snap%20and%20the%20white%20pudding%20was%20unlike%20anything%20I've%20tasted%20in%20years.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221711%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22full%20irish%20breakfast%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7fb29e90c00190890c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221283%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20finished%20Irish%20breakfast.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20white%20pudding%20was%20perfectly%20crumbly%20and%20tasted%20super%20authentic%20%E2%80%94%20it%20honestly%20tasted%20like%20I%20was%20back%20in%20my%20grandparents'%20home.%20The%20bacon%20slices%2C%20or%20rashers%20as%20they're%20sometimes%20called%2C%20were%20perfectly%20browned%20without%20being%20too%20crispy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bacon%20definitely%20wasn't%20as%20greasy%20as%20most%20American%20bacon%20I've%20had%2C%20which%20I%20greatly%20preferred.%20I%20also%20enjoyed%20the%20beans%20on%20toast%20and%20the%20mushrooms%20%E2%80%94%20the%20savory%20flavors%20really%20complemented%20all%20three%20kinds%20of%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20tried%20soda%20bread%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20toasted%20it%20and%20spread%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20the%20Irish%20butter%20on%20top.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22irish%20soda%20bread%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba67829e90c0019088f5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIrish%20soda%20bread%20with%20butter.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20slightly%20sweet%20and%20I%20enjoyed%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20dried%20fruit%20inside.%20However%2C%20I%20think%20I%20preferred%20the%20regular%20toast%2C%20which%20I%20dipped%20in%20the%20sunny-side-up%20eggs%20as%20I%20always%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20only%20ingredient%20on%20my%20plate%20I%20really%20didn't%20like%20was%20the%20grilled%20tomato.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22irish%20breakfast%20tomato%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba7e28f97ab0018751e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cooked%20tomato.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20like%20the%20texture%20and%20thought%20the%20tomato%20slices%20were%20mushy%20and%20unappetizing.%20Something%20about%20a%20warm%20tomato%20just%20didn't%20sit%20right%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20was%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20Irish%20breakfast%20and%20found%20that%20it%20made%20me%20really%20nostalgic%20for%20my%20childhood.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22full%20irish%20breakfast%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F622ba84129e90c00190890d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20finished%20Irish%20breakfast.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scents%20that%20wafted%20through%20my%20kitchen%20combined%20with%20the%20actual%20taste%20of%20the%20food%20instantly%20brought%20me%20back%20to%20my%20grandparents'%20house%20when%20I%20was%20younger.%20I%20haven't%20seen%20my%20grandparents%20in%20many%20years%2C%20but%20this%20meal%20really%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%208%20years%20old%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20definitely%20wouldn't%20go%20to%20the%20trouble%20of%20making%20this%20me