20since%201762%2C%20making%20it%20the%20oldest%20and%20largest%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20Parade%20in%20the%20world.%20According%20to%20the%20organizers%2C%20around%20150%2C000%20people%20march%20every%20year%2C%20and%20the%20parade%20attracts%202%20million%20spectators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20held%20on%20March%2017%20every%20year%20unless%20that%20date%20falls%20on%20a%20Sunday%3B%20in%20that%20case%2C%20it's%20held%20on%20Saturday%2C%20March%2016%2C%20which%20it%20does%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwallethub.com%2Fedu%2Fbest-worst-cities-for-st-patricks-day-celebrations%2F19603%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWalletHub%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20than%2031.3%20million%20Americans%20claim%20they're%20at%20least%20a%20little%20bit%20Irish%2C%20and%20people%20across%20the%20US%20are%20projected%20to%20spend%20%247.2%20billion%20to%20celebrate%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20in%202024.%20New%20York%20City%20is%20a%20particularly%20good%20place%20to%20celebrate%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20the%20most%20Irish%20pubs%20and%20restaurants%20per%20capita%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI've%20spent%20many%20St.%20Patrick's%20Days%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20but%20I%20have%20never%20attended%20the%20parade%2C%20so%20in%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20head%20to%20Manhattan%20and%20check%20it%20out.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22one%20green%20clad%20man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d0b0ed35cc0019e4a18b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20other%20celebrators.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20City%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20but%20I%20grew%20up%20on%20Long%20Island%2C%20and%20I%20happened%20to%20be%20visiting%20my%20family%20on%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20dragged%20my%20mom%20and%20younger%20brother%20with%20me%2C%20and%20we%20headed%20to%20the%20Long%20Island%20Rail%20Road%20to%20catch%20a%20train%20to%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20all%20ready%20for%20the%20train%20to%20be%20packed%20full%20of%20revelers%2C%20but%20it%20was%20actually%20almost%20empty.%20There%20were%20just%20two%20green-clad%20people%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20we%20arrived%20at%20Grand%20Central%20Terminal%2C%20I%20began%20spotting%20more%20people%20who%20were%20festively%20dressed%2C%20including%20some%20holding%20beers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22drinking%20beers%20at%20grand%20central%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d0eaed35cc0019e4a19f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrinking%20beers%20at%20Grand%20Central.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20saw%20more%20people%20dressed%20in%20green%2C%20including%20more%20than%20a%20few%20people%20with%20beers%20and%20other%20drinks.%20One%20group%20of%20guys%20had%20a%20case%20of%20Miller%20all%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20station%20was%20also%20lit%20up%20in%20green%20for%20the%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22grand%20central%20lit%20up%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d14aed35cc0019e4a1d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrand%20Central%20was%20festively%20decorated.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20(relatively)%20new%20LIRR%20terminal%20at%20Grand%20Central%2C%20known%20as%20Grand%20Central%20Madison.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flirr-grand-central-train-11-billion-nyc-abundance-agenda-infrastructure-2023-2%5C%22%3Ecost%20the%20city%20%2411.1%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20construct.%20It%20opened%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20once%20I%20hit%20the%202023%20parade%20route%2C%20things%20started%20to%20go%20downhill.%20I%20started%20from%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parade%20route%20at%20Fifth%20Avenue%20and%2078th%20Street%2C%20and%20it%20was%20already%20crowded.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crowds%20by%20me%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d17bed35cc0019e4a1ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crowds%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parade.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2C%20our%20side%20of%20the%20street%20was.%20The%20other%20side%2C%20the%20park%20side%2C%20could%20be%20a%20little%20deserted%20at%20times%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20across%20as%20far%20as%20I%20could%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parade%20goes%20up%20Fifth%20Avenue%20from%2044th%20Street%20to%2079th%20Street.%20Since%20I%20live%20on%20the%20Upper%20East%20Side%2C%20I%20figured%20we'd%20start%20by%20my%20apartment%20and%20work%20our%20way%20down.%20I'm%20unsure%20if%20that%20was%20the%20best%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20the%20end%20of%20the%20parade%20route%20was%20significantly%20less%20crowded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20walked%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20noticing%20all%20the%20road%20closures%20and%20no%20parking%20signs.%20It%20must%20be%20a%20nightmare%20to%20live%20by%20the%20parade%20route.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22no%20parking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d1ade4a9f30018a6bd35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENo%20parking.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nycstpatricksparade.org%2