lack-out-rage-gallon-tiktok-college-alcohol-poisoning-2023-3%5C%22%3Ethe%20latest%20drink%20craze%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%3A%20The%20name%20stands%20for%20%26quot%3Bblackout%20rage%20gallon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20as%20Business%20Insider%20reported%2C%20they%20caused%20trouble%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversity-massachusetts-borg-drinking-trend-tiktok-viral-video-parties-ambulances-2023-3%5C%22%3Ecollege%20campuses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20journey%2C%20I%20walked%20past%20a%20group%20of%20three%20girls%20each%20holding%20giant%20water%20jugs%20that%20were%20filled%20with%20an%20unidentifiable%20green%20liquid.%20They'd%20written%20%26quot%3BBORG%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20dodging%20tourists%2C%20people%20trying%20to%20sell%20items%20to%20those%20tourists%2C%20and%20some%20people%20who%20seemed%20drunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20didn't%20expect%20it%20to%20get%20political%2C%20but%20between%20a%20group%20at%20Trump%20Tower%2C%20multiple%20signs%20calling%20for%20England%20to%20get%20out%20of%20Ireland%2C%20and%20a%20few%20fliers%20criticizing%20the%20police%20union%20president%2C%20it%20could%20get%20a%20little%20tense.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trump%20tower%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d6b7ed35cc0019e4a36c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20scene%20outside%20Trump%20Tower.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20visit%20to%20last%20year's%20parade%2C%20there%20was%20a%20crowd%20of%20supporters%20waving%20flags%20and%20banners%20with%20%26quot%3BTrump%202024%26quot%3B%20on%20them%20outside%20Trump%20Tower's%20Fifth%20Avenue%20entrance.%20I%20could%20sense%20a%20bit%20of%20unease%20around%20the%20supporters%20as%20they%20were%20yelling%20loudly%20at%20both%20paradegoers%20and%20marchers%2C%20but%20nothing%20ever%20came%20of%20it%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20multiple%20signs%20with%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3BEngland%20Get%20Out%20of%20Ireland%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishcentral.com%2Fopinion%2Fniallodowd%2Fengland-get-out-of-ireland-banner-nyc-patricks-day-parade%5C%22%3EIrish%20Central%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20the%20only%20political%20sign%20allowed%20in%20the%20parade%20proper.%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20it's%20been%20part%20of%20the%20parade%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20posted%20throughout%20the%20parade%20were%20fliers%20criticizing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F01%2F23%2Fpolice-union-president-patrick-lynch-challenged-00079077%5C%22%3EPatrick%20Lynch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20then-police%20union%20president%20and%20an%20aide%20to%20the%20Parade%20Grand%20Marshal.%20Fliers%20said%20he%20should%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20event.%20Lynch%20retired%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20(the%20Police%20Benevolent%20Association%20of%20the%20City%20of%20New%20York)%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20by%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20Neither%20did%20the%20NYC%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day%20Parade%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20we%20got%20closer%20to%20Midtown%2C%20where%20the%20parade%20started%2C%20it%20got%20increasingly%20crowded.%20It%20also%20got%20more%20and%20more%20inconvenient%20to%20keep%20walking%20down%20Fifth%20Avenue%20thanks%20to%20detours.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22detours%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6414d6eeed35cc0019e4a383%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDetours.%3Cp%3EGabbi%20Shaw%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20keep%20walking%20halfway%20down%20the%20bl