er%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhamdirecipes.com%2Fina-garten-shepherds-pie%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecipe%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0calls%20for%20ingredients%20like%20carrots%2C%20celery%2C%20white%20button%20mushrooms%2C%20ground%20turkey%2C%20and%20homemade%20mashed%20potatoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20turned%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20started%20by%20peeling%20my%20Yukon%20gold%20potatoes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peeled%20russet%20potatoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6232214edc43bd001894a7eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeeled%20potatoes.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bag%20of%20potatoes%20typically%20weighs%20around%205%20pounds%2C%20but%20the%20recipe%20only%20called%20for%203%20pounds%20of%20potatoes.%20I%20found%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20that%20this%20was%20the%20perfect%20amount%20to%20fully%20cover%20the%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20then%20chopped%20the%20potatoes%20into%201-inch%20cubes%20and%20placed%20them%20in%20a%20pot%20with%20water.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peeled%20and%20chopped%20russet%20potatoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62322157843ef30018e758d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeeled%20and%20chopped%20potatoes.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20simmered%20the%20potatoes%20until%20they%20were%20tender.%20This%20took%20about%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20used%20a%20time-saving%20hack%20to%20prepare%20my%20vegetables.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chopped%20vegetables%20in%20a%20small%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62322161843ef30018e758da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChopped%20vegetables.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recipe%20called%20for%20finely%20diced%20carrots%2C%20celery%2C%20and%20white%20button%20mushrooms.%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20food%20processor%20to%20easily%20chop%20up%20my%20vegetables.%20I%20liked%20the%20end%20result%20and%20found%20this%20was%20the%20simplest%20way%20to%20prepare%20all%20the%20vegetables%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20hand-chopped%20some%20mushrooms%20to%20add%20more%20texture.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chopped%20vegetables%20in%20a%20small%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62322168dc43bd001894a7f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMushrooms.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20vegetables%20were%20chopped%2C%20I%20set%20them%20aside%20in%20a%20small%20bowl%20and%20turned%20my%20attention%20towards%20cooking%20the%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20recipe%20calls%20for%201.5%20pounds%20of%20ground%20turkey%20meat%2C%20but%20you%20can%20get%20creative%20if%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20use%20turkey.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223071%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cooked%20ground%20turkey%20meat%20in%20a%20large%20saute%20pan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62322232843ef30018e75929%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECooked%20ground%20turkey%20meat.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20use%20practically%20any%20kind%20of%20ground%20meat%20you%20would%20like%2C%20or%20even%20plant-based%20ground%20meat%20if%20you're%20vegetarian.%20I%20ended%20up%20liking%20the%20choice%20of%20