red%20to%20come%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20office%20at%20least%2039%20days%20a%20quarter%20%E2%80%94%20the%20equivalent%20of%20about%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20internal%20documents%20seen%20by%20BI%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20want%20to%20keep%20working%20from%20home%2C%20staff%20can%20opt%20to%20go%20fully%20remote.%20But%20that%20option%20has%20a%20downside%3A%20fully%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-from-home-remote-work-increased-layoff-risk-job-market-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20not%20be%20considered%20for%20promotion%2C%20or%20be%20able%20to%20change%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20remote%20team%20members%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20the%20trade-offs%3A%20Career%20advancement%2C%20including%20applying%20to%20new%20roles%20in%20the%20company%2C%20will%20require%20a%20team%20member%20to%20reclassify%20as%20hybrid%20onsite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20company%20has%20been%20complaining%20about%20this%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20Dell%20staffer%2C%20who%20works%20alongside%20senior%20management.%20The%20employee%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20reprisals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bin-person%20connections%20paired%20with%20a%20flexible%20approach%20are%20critical%20to%20drive%20innovation%20and%20value%20differentiation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20differs%20from%20founder%20and%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-of-michael-dell-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20Dell's%3C%2Fa%3E%20previous%20support%20for%20remote%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20told%20CRN%20that%20the%20company's%20expanded%20homeworking%20culture%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20here%20to%20stay.%26quot%3B%20The%20billionaire%20lat