han%20at%20home%2C%20even%20though%20there's%20no%20evidence%20to%20back%20that%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20%26quot%3Bpack%20mentality%26quot%3B%20at%20play%2C%20says%20Cooper%2C%20with%20tech%20companies%20trying%20to%20follow%20what%20everybody%20else%20is%20doing%2C%20rather%20than%20continue%20with%20what%20has%20worked%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20on%20the%20chopping%20block%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrustrated%20workers%20at%20Dell%20spoke%20out%20anonymously%20to%20BI%20about%20how%20the%20new%20policy%20will%20affect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20being%20forced%20into%20a%20position%20where%20either%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20staying%20as%20the%20low%20man%20on%20the%20totem%20pole%2C%20first%20on%20the%20chopping%20block%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20workforce%20reduction%2C%20or%20we%20can%20be%20hybrid%20and%20go%20in%20multiple%20days%20a%20week%2C%20which%20really%20affects%20a%20lot%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20staffer%20said%20she%20and%20many%20colleagues%20were%20hired%20on%20remote%20contracts%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20worker%20lives%20about%20a%2045-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20nearest%20office%20and%20works%2010-hour%20shifts%20four%20days%20a%20week.%20However%2C%20traveling%20there%20would%20be%20virtually%20impossible%20given%20she%20no%20longer%20drives%20following%20a%20car%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20many%20of%20her%20colleagues%20would%20find%20it%20very%20challenging%20to%20get%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Approved'%20offices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Dell%20worker%20is%20already%20feeling%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20new%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell's%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20sites%20includes%2017%20offices%20in%20the%20US%20and%2026%20globally%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20the%20senior%20employee's%20nearest%20office.%20%26quot%3BI%20now%20know%20I%20have%20no%20office.%20So%20I%20am%20remote%2C%20or%20I%20move%20if%20I%20want%20to%20stay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20viewed%20a%20promotion%20offer%20sent%20to%20the%20long-serving%20remote%20worker%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-mandates-creating-huge-disruption-in-workers-lives-experts-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERTO%20mandate%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20accept%20that%20promotion%2C%20the%20employee%20would%20not%20only%20have%20to%20start%20coming%20into%20the%20office%2C%20but%20move%20state%20to%20be%20near%20an%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20Round%20Rock%20Texas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d765dbf533b039a885f016%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDell's%20HQ%20in%20Round%20Rock%20Texas%20is%20one%20of%2017%20offices%20approved%20for%20general%20employees.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EGeographically%20divided%20teams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20also%20say%20that%20Dell's%20claims%20about%20fostering%20%26quot%3Bin-person%20connection%26quot%3B%20do%20not%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20for%20teams%20at%20Dell%20to%20be%20spread%20around%20the%20US%20and%20even%20other%20countries%2C%20according%20to%20BI's%20senior%20source%20at%20Dell%2C%20who%20works%20across%20the%20organization%20and%20has%20access%20to%20employee%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20team%20has%20people%20in%20at%20least%20two%20states%2C%20some%20in%20three%20or%20four.%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20one%20team%20where%20everyone%20is%20in%20one%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20even%20if%20commuting%20distances%20are%20feasible%2C%20many%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20collaborate%20face-to-face%2