dmother%2C%20Buri%20Bai%2C%20was%20awarded%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20preservation%20efforts.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20carry%20forward%20her%20legacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20shares%20that%20the%20family%20starts%20the%20work%20nearly%20eight%20months%20before%20Samvaad%20as%20it%20takes%2010%20days%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20She%20happily%20adds%20that%20their%20paintings%20sell%20like%20hotcakes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stall%20displaying%20products%20featuring%20Warli%20art.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsankalp_foundation_warli_art_11zon-1710328090-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344727%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20stall%20displaying%20various%20products%20featuring%20Warli%20art.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stalls%20away%20is%20Dinabandhu%20Soren%20from%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ho%20tribe.%20It%20is%20his%20ninth%20year%20at%20Samvaad%2C%20and%20each%20year%20has%20been%20fruitful%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSelling%20our%20paintings%20was%20a%20loss-making%20business%20in%20Ganjam%20district%20till%20we%20learnt%20about%20Samvaad.%20The%20workshops%20helped%20create%20a%20balance%20between%20our%20traditional%20painting%20techniques%20and%20the%20market%20demands.%20With%20a%20few%20tweaks%20and%20the%20right%20market%20linkages%2C%20we%20sold%20%3Cem%3Egond%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohra%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejuang%3C%2Fem%3E%20paintings%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20across%20India.%20We%20were%20even%20selected%20to%20do%20live%20sketching%20at%20G20%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20an%20art%20teacher%20at%20Srujanika%2C%20a%20women-led%20self-help%20group.%20Srujanika%20has%2030%20women%20who%20make%20paintings%2C%20Army%20uniforms%2C%20and%20other%20merchandise%20like%20%3Cem%3Edupattas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20T-shirts%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20profits%2C%20the%20women%20are%20passing%20on%20the%20skills%20to%20their%20children%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYazile%20from%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Rengma%20tribe%20has%20a%20similar%20journey%2C%20from%20no%20sales%20to%20selling%20pan%20India.%20%E2%80%9CNearly%20every%20homemaker%20in%20the%20Dimapur%20area%20can%20make%20our%20traditional%20attire%2C%20%3Cem%3Emekhelas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20shawls.%20The%20skills%20were%20there%2C%20but%20the%20selling%20opportunity%20was%20missing.%20We%20attended%20a%20workshop%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20learned%20that%20new%20designs%20can%20be%20implemented%20on%20pillow%20covers%2C%20cushion%20covers%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20etc.%20In%20our%20second%20year%2C%20we%20did%20that%20and%20made%20profits.%20I%20also%20made%20friends%20from%20other%20tribal%20communities%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20fashion%20trends%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yazile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20and%20craft%20workshops%20helped%20artists%20like%20Yazile%20and%20Dinabandhu%20post-pandemic%20when%20the%20market%20crashed%20and%20selling%20at%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecame%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20building%20online%20market%20links%20for%2026%20tribal%20communities%20representing%2030%20art%20forms.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3EToda%3C%2Fem%3E%20embroidery%20of%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Cem%3EMuga%20%3C%2Fem%3Esilk%20of%20Assam%2C%20and%20more%20as%20popular%20as%20%3Cem%3EBanarasi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIkat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChikankari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20brought%20in%20experts%20from%20NIFT%20and%20NID%20to%20impart%20the%20skills%2C%20colour%20combinations%2C%20motifs%2C%20etc%2C%20that%20meet%20customer%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrends%20in%20the%20metro%20change%20fast%2C%20so%20we%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20change%20their%20cultural%20identity.%C2%A0%20But%20they%20can%20experiment%20with%20colours%20and%20motifs.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20pastel%20colour%20is%20in%20the%20market%2C%20infuse%20those%20colours%20in%20the%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thronging%20crowds%20at%20handicraft%20stalls%20were%20proof%20that%20the%20workshops%20were%20beneficial.%20Chaaya%20Saraiwala%2C%20an%20attendee%2C%20purchased%20Yazile%E2%80%99s%20shawls%20and%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20fridge%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20attending%20Samvaad%20and%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20the%20myriad%20products%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20our%20country.%20I%20have%20bought%20a%20few%20items%20for%20my%20family.%20Each%20product%20has%20a%20story%20to%20tell.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20history%20that%20we%20do%20not%20know%2C%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20conclaves%20like%20Samvaad%20are%20changing%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Samvaad%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710249302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_0955-1710328096.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344574%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Tata%20Samvaad%20conclave%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20artisans%20from%20indigenous%20tribes%20across%20India%20shone%20a%20spotlight%20on%20fading%20tribal%20arts%2C%20reviving%20them%20with%20contemporary%20flair%20to%20build%20livelihoods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trader%20Joe%E2%80%99s%20Threatened%20Workers%20Ahead%20Of%20Union%20Vote%2C%20Feds%20Allege%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Labor%20board%20officials%20have%20accused%20the%20grocer%20of%20using%20illegal%20tactics%20to%20sway%20workers%20against%20unionizing.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710209921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65a2ecd0240000310027f382.jpeg%3Fcache%3Dg8sPa742ew%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Labor%20board%20officials%20have%20accused%20the%20grocer%20of%20using%20illegal%20tactics%20to%20sway%20workers%20against%20unionizing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A265%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftrader-joes-accused-threatening-workers-labor-board_n_65ef8ab2e4b05cfcf680b337%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Unique%20Conclave%20Celebrates%20The%20Cultural%20Wealth%20of%20200%20Tribes%20of%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%93%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20next%20to%20women%20dressed%20in%20colourful%20sarees%2C%20Pritesh%20Kumar%20Khalko%20looked%20out%20of%20place%20at%20first%20in%20his%20black%20jacket%20at%20Jamshedpur%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20He%20looked%20tired%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20from%20excitedly%20inviting%20strangers%20to%20his%20food%20stall%20and%20narrating%20the%20fascinating%20story%20behind%20each%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ebaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bamboo)%20pickle%20is%20good%20for%20your%20blood%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehau%20%3C%2Fem%3Echutney%20made%20from%20red%20weaver%20ants%20is%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20calcium.%20%3Cem%3EJamun%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%20helps%20control%20sugar%3B%20you%20will%20not%20find%20this%20anywhere%20else%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20potential%20customer%20at%20his%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conviction%20in%20his%20tone%20changed%20as%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20team%20asked%20about%20how%20his%20community%20cuisine%20could%20help%20his%20tribe%20do%20better.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CProvide%20us%20platforms%20like%20Samvaad%20where%20we%20can%20share%20our%20culture%20and%20food%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20help%20us%20tell%20our%20own%20stories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20preserving%20his%20tribal%20identity%20through%20cuisine%20mirrored%20the%20essence%20of%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20(TSF)%2C%20which%20brings%20together%20the%20diverse%20tribes%20of%20India%20on%20one%20platform%20for%20a%20five-day-long%20festivity%2C%20which%20lets%20everyone%20immerse%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274494%2Fgond-artist-artwork-museums-france-usa-uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20belongs%20to%20one%20of%20the%20200%20tribal%20communities%20participating%20in%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20tribal%20conclave%20which%20brings%20together%20tribes%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20beyond.%20It%20is%20emerging%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20platforms%20for%20dialogues%20on%20tribal%20discourse%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Performance%20at%20Samvaad%20on%20Gopal%20Maidan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-