-4-1709877672.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-4-1709877672-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-4-1709877672-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-4-1709877672-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fwomens-day-4-1709877672-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344319%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELooking%20at%20her%20transformation%20from%20the%20old%20days%2C%20Priya%20wishes%20to%20encourage%20other%20women%20like%20her.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20Thursday%2C%20I%20move%20all%20my%20furniture%20aside%20to%20keep%20all%20the%20fruits%20for%20packaging.%20My%20young%20children%20also%20pitch%20in%20to%20deliver%20orders%20on%20their%20bicycles%20and%20earn%20Rs%205-10%20per%20delivery.%20With%20this%2C%20my%20children%20are%20also%20learning%20the%20basics%20of%20entrepreneurship%2C%20the%20value%20of%20money%2C%20and%20above%20all%20importance%20of%20inclusive%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashi%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20every%20Thursday%2C%20she%20pitches%20in%20the%20household%20chores%20so%20that%20Priya%20has%20time%20to%20cater%20to%20all%20the%20orders.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20not%20been%20a%20single%20day%20when%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20hot%20food.%20Priya%20makes%20sure%20that%20this%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20affect%20household%20duties.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20would%20worry%20about%20how%20they%E2%80%99ll%20fend%20for%20themselves%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20savings.%20But%20today%2C%20I%20take%20pride%20that%20Priya%20has%20earned%20financial%20freedom%20as%20well%20as%20popularity.%20She%20is%20so%20enthusiastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%