ion%20of%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20kids%20love%20theatre%20sessions%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfident%20and%20outgoing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20encourages%20them%20to%20speak%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20great%20because%20we%20noticed%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20shy%20and%20reluctant%20to%20speak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%201.30%20pm%20when%20the%20kids%20file%20to%20go%20back%20home%2C%20brighter%20than%20the%20smile%20on%20any%20of%20their%20faces%2C%20is%20the%20one%20on%20their%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENisha%2C%20who%20has%20been%20with%20Nayi%20Disha%20since%20it%20started%2C%20is%20Seema%E2%80%99s%20rock.%20%E2%80%9CSeema%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20teacher%20and%20someone%20put%20me%20in%20touch%20with%20her.%20Since%20the%20start%2C%20I%20have%20been%20teaching%20these%20children%20many%20subjects%20and%20have%20watched%20these%20children%20grow.%20I%20remember%20them%20being%20unruly%2C%20but%20with%20time%2C%20we%20taught%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332617%2Fias-officers-share-revision-tips-tricks-techniques-upsc-cse-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eetiquette%20and%20manners%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20other%20subjects.%20They%20have%20picked%20these%20things%20up%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Feducating-underprivileged-kids-6-1709817898.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22